- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-853">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-853">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-854">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-854">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-855">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-855">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-856">testacs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-856">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-857">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-857">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-858">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-858">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-859">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-859">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-iaas-database-connection-string-and-azure-sql-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-860">Строка подключения к базе данных Azure IAAS и строка подключения Azure SQL Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-860">Azure IAAS database connection string and Azure SQL connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-861">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-861">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-862">Строка "Server", "server" или "data source", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, включая строку "cloudapp.azure".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-862">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-863">com или cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-863">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-864">net" или "database.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-864">net" or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-865">net и строку "Password", "password" или "pwd".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-865">net", and the string "Password" or "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-866">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-866">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-867">строка "Server", "server" или "data source"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-867">the string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-868">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-868">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-869">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-869">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-870">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-870">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-871">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-871">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-872">Строка "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-872">The string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-873">com, "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-873">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-874">net или database.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-874">net", or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-875">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-875">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-876">любое сочетание от 1 до 300 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-876">any combination of between 1-300 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-877">строка "Password", "password" или "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-877">the string "Password", "password", or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-878">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-878">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-879">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-879">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-880">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-880">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-881">один или несколько символов, которые не являются точками с запоем (;), кавычка (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-881">one or more characters that aren't a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-882">точка с зачетом (;), кавычка (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-882">a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-883">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-883">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-884">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-884">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-885">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-885">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-886">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-886">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-887">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-887">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-888">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-888">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IAAS Database Connection String and Azure SQL Connection String-->
<Entity id="ce1a126d-186f-4700-8c0c-486157b953fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-889">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-889">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-890">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-890">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-891">(Технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-891">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-894">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-894">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-895">песочница</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-895">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-896">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-896">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-897">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-897">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-898">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-898">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-899">testacs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-899">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-900">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-900">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-901">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-901">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-902">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-902">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-903">Строка подключения Azure IoT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-903">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-904">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-904">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-905">Строка HostName, за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, включая строки "azure-devices".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-905">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-906">net" и "SharedAccessKey".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-906">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-907">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-907">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-908">строка "HostName"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-908">the string "HostName"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-909">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-909">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-910">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-910">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-911">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-911">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-912">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-912">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-913">строка "azure-devices.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-913">the string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-914">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-914">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-915">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-915">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-916">строка "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-916">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-917">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-917">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-918">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-918">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-919">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-919">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-920">любое сочетание 43 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-920">any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-921">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-921">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-922">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-922">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-923">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-923">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-924">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-924">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-925">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-925">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-926">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-926">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-927">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-927">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IoT Connection String-->
<Entity id="0b34bec3-d5d6-4974-b7b0-dcdb5c90c29d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-928">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-928">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-929">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-929">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-930">(Технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-930">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-931">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-931">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-932">fabrikam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-932">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-933">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-933">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-934">песочница</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-934">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-935">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-935">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-936">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-936">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-937">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-937">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-938">testacs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-938">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-939">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-939">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-940">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-940">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-941">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-941">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-publish-setting-password"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-942">Пароль параметра публикации Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-942">Azure publish setting password</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-943">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-943">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-944">Строка "userpwd=", за которой следует букво-цифровая строка.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-944">The string "userpwd=" followed by an alphanumeric string.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-945">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-945">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-946">строка "userpwd="</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-946">the string "userpwd="</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-947">любая комбинация из 60 строчная букв или цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-947">any combination of 60 lowercase letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-948">кавычка ("")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-948">a quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-949">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-949">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-950">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-950">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-951">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-951">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-952">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-952">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-953">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-953">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-954">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-954">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
<!--Azure Publish Setting Password-->
<Entity id="75f4cc8a-a68e-49e5-89ce-fa8f03d286a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
       <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords" />
       <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
           <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
       </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-955">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-955">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-956">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-956">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

## <a name="azure-redis-cache-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-969">Строка подключения кэша Azure Redis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-969">Azure Redis cache connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-970">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-970">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-971">Строка redis.cache.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-971">The string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-972">net, за которыми следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенной ниже схеме, включая строку "password" или "pwd".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-972">net" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-973">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-973">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-974">строка redis.cache.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-974">the string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-975">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-975">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-976">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-976">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-977">строка "password" или "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-977">the string "password" or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-978">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-978">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-979">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-979">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-980">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-980">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-981">любое сочетание 43 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком "плюс" (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-981">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-982">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-982">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-983">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-983">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-984">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-984">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-985">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-985">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-986">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-986">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-987">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-987">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-988">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-988">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Redis Cache Connection String-->
<Entity id="095a7e6c-efd8-46d5-af7b-5298d53a49fc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-990">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-990">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-991">(Технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-991">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-992">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-992">contoso</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-994">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-994">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-995">песочница</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-995">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-996">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-996">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-997">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-997">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-998">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-998">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-999">testacs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-999">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1000">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1000">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1001">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1001">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1002">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1002">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-sas"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1003">Azure SAS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1003">Azure SAS</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1004">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1004">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1005">Строка "sig", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в шаблоне ниже.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1005">The string "sig" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1006">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1006">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1007">строка "sig"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1007">the string "sig"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1008">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1008">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1009">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1009">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1010">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1010">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1011">любое сочетание между 43–53 символами, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами или знаком процента (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1011">any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1012">строка "%3d"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1012">the string "%3d"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1013">любой символ, который не является буквой нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрой или знаком процента (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1013">any character that isn't a lower- or uppercase letter, digit, or percent sign (%)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1014">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1014">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1015">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1015">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1016">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1016">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1017">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1017">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1018">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureSAS находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1018">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure SAS-->
<Entity id="4d235014-e564-47f4-a6fb-6ebb4a826834" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-service-bus-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1019">Строка подключения к шине обслуживания Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1019">Azure service bus connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1020">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1020">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1021">Строка "EndPoint", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенной ниже схеме, включая строки "servicebus.windows".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1021">The string "EndPoint" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1022">net" и "SharedAccesKey".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1022">net" and "SharedAccesKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1023">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1023">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1024">строка "EndPoint"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1024">the string "EndPoint"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1025">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1025">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1026">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1026">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1027">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1027">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1028">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1028">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1029">строка "servicebus.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1029">the string "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1030">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1030">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1031">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1031">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1032">строка "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1032">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1033">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1033">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1034">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1034">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1035">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1035">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1036">любое сочетание 43 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком "плюс" (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1036">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1037">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1037">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1038">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1038">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1039">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1039">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1040">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1040">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1041">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1041">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1042">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1042">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1043">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1043">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Service Bus Connection String-->
<Entity id="b9a6578f-a83f-4fcd-bf44-2130bae49a6f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1044">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1044">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1045">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1045">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1046">(Технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1046">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1047">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1047">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1048">fabrikam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1048">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1049">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1049">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1050">песочница</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1050">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1051">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1051">onebox</span></span>

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1058">Ключ учетной записи хранения Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1058">Azure storage account key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1059">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1059">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1060">Строка "DefaultEndpointsProtocol", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенной ниже схеме, включая строку AccountKey.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1060">The string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "AccountKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1061">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1061">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1062">строка "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1062">the string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1063">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1063">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1064">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1064">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1065">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1065">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1066">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1066">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1067">строка AccountKey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1067">the string "AccountKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1068">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1068">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1069">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1069">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1070">от нуля до двух символов в белом пространстве</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1070">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1071">любое сочетание 86 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком "плюс" (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1071">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1072">два знака равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1072">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1073">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1073">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1074">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1074">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1075">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1075">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1076">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1076">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1077">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1077">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1078">Регулярное выражение CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1078">The regular expression CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1079">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1079">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key-->
<Entity id="c7bc98e8-551a-4c35-a92d-d2c8cda714a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1080">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1080">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1085">(Технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1085">(Technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key-generic"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1097">Ключ учетной записи хранилища Azure (универсальный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1097">Azure Storage account key (generic)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1098">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1098">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1099">Любое сочетание 86 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+), предшествующего или за которым следуют символы, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1099">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1100">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1100">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1101">от нуля до одного из символов больше чем (>), апострофа ('), знака равного (=), кавычка (") или знака числа (#)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1101">zero to one of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1102">любое сочетание 86 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком "плюс" (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1102">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1103">два знака равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1103">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1104">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1104">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1105">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1105">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1106">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1106">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1107">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1107">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1108">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1108">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1109">Номер водительского удостоверения для Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1109">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1110">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1110">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1111">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1111">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1112">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1112">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1113">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1113">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1114">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1114">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1115">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1115">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1116">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1116">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1117">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1117">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1118">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1118">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1119">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1119">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Belgium Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d89fd329-9324-433c-b687-2c37bd5166f3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1252">Национальный номер для Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1252">Belgium national number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1253">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1253">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1254">11 цифр, а также необязательные селитари</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1254">11 digits plus optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1255">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1255">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1256">11 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1256">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1257">шесть цифр и два необязательных периода в формате YY. MM.DD для даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1257">six digits and two optional periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1258">Необязательный выбор точки, тире, пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1258">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1259">три последовательной цифры (нечетные для самцов, даже для самок)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1259">three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1260">Необязательный выбор точки, тире, пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1260">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1261">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1261">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1262">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1262">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1263">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1263">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1264">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1264">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1265">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1265">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1266">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1266">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1267">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_belgium_national_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1267">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1268">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1268">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1269">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1269">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1270">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1270">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1271">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1271">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
       <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1272">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1272">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1330">Номер паспорта гражданина Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1330">Belgium passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1331">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1331">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1332">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1332">two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1333">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1333">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1334">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1334">two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1335">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1335">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1336">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1336">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1337">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1337">Definition</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1338">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1338">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1339">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1339">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1340">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1340">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1341">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date2` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YY или ключевое слово из `Keywords_eu_passport_date` или `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` найдено</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1341">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1342">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1342">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1343">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1343">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1344">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1344">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d7b1315b-21ca-4774-a32a-596010ff78fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="belgium-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1371">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1371">Belgium value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1372">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1372">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1373">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1373">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1374">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1374">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1375">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1375">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1376">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1376">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1377">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1377">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1378">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1378">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1379">12-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1379">12-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1380">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1380">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1381">12-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1381">12-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1382">буква B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1382">a letter B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1383">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1383">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1384">цифра 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1384">a digit 0</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1385">цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1385">a digit from 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1386">необязательная точка, дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1386">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1387">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1387">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1388">необязательная точка, дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1388">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1389">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1389">four digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1390">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1390">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1391">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1391">Yes</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1392">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1392">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1393">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1393">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1394">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1394">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1395">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1395">A keyword from Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1396">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1396">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1397">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1397">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="85b5b3c3-f2de-4ae8-ac46-fd3cb38bf9ed" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1398">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1398">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1399">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1399">Keyword_belgium_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1400">nº tva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1400">nº tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1401">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1401">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1402">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1402">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1403">numéro t.v.a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1403">numéro t.v.a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1404">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1404">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1405">umsatzsteuernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1405">umsatzsteuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1406">btw</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1406">btw</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1407">btw #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1407">btw#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1408">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1408">vat#</span></span>


## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1409">Номер CPF для Бразилии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1409">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1410">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1410">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1411">11 цифр, которые включают проверочную цифру и могут быть форматированными или неформатированными.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1411">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1412">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1412">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1413">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1413">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1414">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1414">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1415">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1415">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1416">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1416">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1417">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1417">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1418">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1418">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1419">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1419">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1420">две цифры, которые являются провероными цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1420">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1421">Неформатированные:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1421">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1422">11 цифр, где две последние цифры — проверочные.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1422">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1423">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1423">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1424">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1424">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1425">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1425">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1426">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1426">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1427">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1427">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1428">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cpf;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1428">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1429">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1429">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1430">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1430">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1431">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1431">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1432">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1432">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1441">Identificação</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1441">Identificação</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1442">Inscrição</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1442">Inscrição</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1443">Receita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1443">Receita</span></span> 

   
## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1444">Номер юридического лица для Бразилии (CNPJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1444">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1445">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1445">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1446">14 цифр, которые включают регистрационный номер, номер филиала и проверочные цифры, а также разделители.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1446">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1447">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1447">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1448">14 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1448">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1449">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1449">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1450">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1450">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1451">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1451">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1452">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1452">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1453">три цифры (эти первые восемь цифр являются регистрационным номером)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1453">three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1454">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1454">a forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1455">четырехзначный номер филиала</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1455">four-digit branch number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1456">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1456">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1457">две цифры, которые являются провероными цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1457">two digits that are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1458">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1458">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1459">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1459">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1460">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1460">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1461">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1461">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1462">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1462">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1463">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cnpj;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1463">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1464">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1464">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1465">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1465">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1466">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1466">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1467">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1467">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1469">Keyword_brazil_cnpj</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1469">Keyword_brazil_cnpj</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1479">Company</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1479">Company</span></span>
