## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1489">Национальный идентификационный номер для Бразилии (RG)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1489">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1490">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1490">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1491">Registro Geral (старый формат): девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1491">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1492">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (новый формат): 11 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1492">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1493">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1493">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1494">Registro Geral (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1494">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1495">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1495">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1496">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1496">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1497">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1497">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1498">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1498">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1499">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1499">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1500">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1500">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1501">одна цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1501">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1502">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1502">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1503">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1503">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1504">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1504">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1505">одна цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1505">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1506">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1506">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1507">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1507">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1508">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1508">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1509">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1509">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1510">функция Func_brazil_rg находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1510">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1511">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_rg;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1511">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1512">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1512">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
      <Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1513">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1513">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_brazil_rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1514">Keyword_brazil_rg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1514">Keyword_brazil_rg</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1515">Cédula de identidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1515">Cédula de identidade</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1516">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1516">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1517">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1517">national id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1518">número de rregistro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1518">número de rregistro</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1519">registro de Iidentidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1519">registro de Iidentidade</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1520">registro geral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1520">registro geral</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1521">RG (это ключевое слово с чувствительностью к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1521">RG (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1522">RIC (это ключевое слово с чувствительностью к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1522">RIC (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span> 


## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1523">Номер водительского удостоверения для Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1523">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1524">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1524">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1525">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1525">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1526">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1526">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1527">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1527">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1528">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1528">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1529">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1529">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1530">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1530">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1531">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1531">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1532">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1532">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1533">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1533">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="66d39258-94c2-43b2-804b-aa312258e54b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>    
```

## <a name="bulgaria-uniform-civil-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1660">Однородный номер для Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1660">Bulgaria uniform civil number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1661">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1661">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1662">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1662">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1663">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1663">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1664">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1664">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1665">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1665">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1666">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1666">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1667">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1667">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1668">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1668">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1669">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1669">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1670">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1670">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1671">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1671">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1672">две цифры, соответствующие порядку рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1672">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1673">одна цифра, соответствующая полу: четная цифра для самца и нечетная цифра для женщина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1673">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1674">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1674">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1675">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1675">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1676">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1676">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1677">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1677">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1678">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1678">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1679">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1679">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1680">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1680">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1681">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1681">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1682">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1682">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1723">униформ граждански не</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1723">униформ граждански не</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1724">униформ граждански номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1724">униформ граждански номер</span></span>

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1727">Номер паспорта гражданина Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1727">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1728">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1728">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1729">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1729">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1730">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1730">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1731">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1731">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1732">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1732">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1733">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1733">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1734">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1734">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1735">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1735">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1736">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1736">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1737">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1737">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1738">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_eu_passport_date1` ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1738">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1739">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1739">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1740">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1740">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1741">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1741">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="f7172b82-c588-4216-845e-4e54e397f29a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1742">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1742">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1743">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1743">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1746">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1746">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1747">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1747">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1748">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1748">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1749">passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1749">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1750">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1750">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1751">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1751">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1752">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1752">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1753">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1753">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1754">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1754">Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1755">номер на паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1755">номер на паспорта</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1756">номер на паспорт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1756">номер на паспорт</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1757">No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1757">паспорт №</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1759">дата проблемы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1759">date of issue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1760">дата окончания срока действия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1760">date of expiry</span></span>

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1761">Номер банковского счета для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1761">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1762">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1762">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1763">7 или 12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1763">7 or 12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1764">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1764">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1765">Номер банковского счета для Канады — 7 или 12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1765">A Canada Bank Account Number is 7 or 12 digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1766">Транзитный номер банковского счета в Канаде имеет указанный ниже формат.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1766">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1767">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1767">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1768">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1768">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1769">три цифры ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1769">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1770">ноль "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1770">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1771">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1771">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1772">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1772">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1773">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1773">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1774">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1774">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1775">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1775">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1776">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1776">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1777">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1777">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1778">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1778">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1779">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1779">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1780">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1780">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1781">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1781">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1805">Номер водительского удостоверения для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1805">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1806">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1806">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1807">Зависит от провинции.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1807">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1808">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1808">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1809">Различные шаблоны, соответствующие провинциям Альберта, Британская Колумбия, Манитоба, Нью-Брансуик, Ньюфаундленд и Лабрадор, Новая Шотландия, Онтарио, Остров Принца Эдуарда, Квебек и Саскачеван.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1809">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1810">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1810">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1811">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1811">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1812">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1812">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1813">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1813">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1814">функция Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1814">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1815">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1815">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1816">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1816">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="37186abb-8e48-4800-ad3c-e3d1610b3db0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_alberta_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_alberta_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
```

## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1952">Номер службы здравоохранения для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1952">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1953">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1953">Format</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1954">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1954">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1955">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1955">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1956">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1956">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1957">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1957">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1958">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1958">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1959">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1959">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1960">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1960">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1961">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_health_service_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1961">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1962">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_health_service_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1962">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1974">Номер паспорта гражданина Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1974">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1975">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1975">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1976">две буквы в верхнем регистре, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1976">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1977">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1977">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1978">две буквы в верхнем регистре, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1978">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1979">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1979">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1980">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1980">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1981">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1981">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1982">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1982">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1983">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1983">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-1984">Находится ключевое слово Keyword_canada_passport_number или Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-1984">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2014">Персональный идентификационный номер медицинского удостоверения для Канады (PHIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2014">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2015">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2015">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2016">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2016">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2017">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2017">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2018">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2018">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2019">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2019">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2020">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2020">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2021">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2021">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2022">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2022">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2023">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_phin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2023">The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2024">Найдено по крайней мере два ключевых Keyword_canada_phin или Keyword_canada_provinces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2024">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2057">Номер социального страхования для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2057">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2058">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2058">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2059">девять цифр с необязательными дефисами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2059">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2060">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2060">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2061">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2061">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2062">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2062">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2063">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2063">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2064">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2064">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2065">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2065">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2066">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2066">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2067">Неформатированные: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2067">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2068">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2068">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2069">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2069">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2070">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2070">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2071">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2071">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2072">Функция Func_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2072">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2073">Выполняются по меньшей мере два из таких условий:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2073">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2074">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2074">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2075">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2075">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2076">функция Func_eu_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2076">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2077">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2077">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2078">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2078">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2079">функция Func_unformatted_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2079">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2080">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2080">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2081">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2081">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2106">Номер удостоверения личности для Чили</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2106">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2107">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2107">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2108">от семи до восьми цифр, а также делегировка контрольной цифры или буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2108">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2109">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2109">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2110">семь–восемь цифр, а также делегаторы:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2110">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2111">одна–две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2111">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2112">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2112">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2113">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2113">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2114">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2114">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2115">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2115">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2116">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2116">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2117">одна цифра или буква (без чувствительность к букве), которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2117">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2118">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2118">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2119">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2119">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2120">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2120">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2121">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2121">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2122">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2122">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2123">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_chile_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2123">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2124">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2124">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2125">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2125">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2126">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2126">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2127">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2127">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2162">Номер удостоверения для Чили</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2162">Chile identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2163">Удостоверение чили #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2163">Chile identity #</span></span>

   
## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2164">Номер удостоверения личности резидента Китая (КНР)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2164">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2165">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2165">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2166">18 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2166">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2167">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2167">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2168">18 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2168">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2169">шесть цифр, которые являются кодом адреса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2169">six digits that are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2170">восемь цифр в виде YYYYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2170">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2171">три цифры, которые являются кодом заказа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2171">three digits that are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2172">одна цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2172">one digit that is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2173">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2173">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2174">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2174">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2175">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2175">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2176">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2176">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2177">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2177">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2178">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_china_resident_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2178">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2179">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2179">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2180">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2180">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2181">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2181">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2182">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2182">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2183">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2183">Keywords</span></span>

### <a name="keyword_china_resident_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2184">Keyword_china_resident_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2184">Keyword_china_resident_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2185">Resident Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2185">Resident Identity Card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2187">National Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2187">National Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2188">身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2188">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2189">居民 身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2189">居民 身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2190">居民身份证</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2190">居民身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2191">鉴定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2191">鉴定</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2192">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2192">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2193">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2193">居民 身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2194">鑑定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2194">鑑定</span></span> 

   
## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2195">Номер кредитной карты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2195">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2196">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2196">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2197">От 14 до 16 цифр, которые могут быть отформатированы или неформатированы (dddddddd), и которые должны пройти проверку Luhn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2197">14 to 16 digits that can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and that must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2198">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2198">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2199">Сложный и надежный шаблон, который обнаруживает карточки от всех основных торговых марок по всему миру, включая Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, карточки для карточек.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2199">Complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2200">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2200">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2201">Да (рассчитывается по алгоритму Луна).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2201">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2202">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2202">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2203">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2203">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2204">Функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2204">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2205">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2205">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2206">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_verification;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2206">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2207">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2207">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2208">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2208">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2209">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2209">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2210">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2210">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2211">функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2211">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2212">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2212">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2472">Номер водительского удостоверения для Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2472">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2473">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2473">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2474">восемь цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2474">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2475">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2475">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2476">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2476">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2477">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2477">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2478">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2478">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2479">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2479">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2480">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2480">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2481">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2481">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2482">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2482">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="005b3ef1-47dd-4e68-bb02-c6db484d00f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2606">Номер удостоверения личности для Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2606">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2607">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации для национального идентификационных номеров ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2607">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2608">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2608">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2609">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2609">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2610">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2610">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2611">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2611">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2612">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2612">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2613">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2613">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2614">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2614">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2615">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2615">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2616">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2616">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2617">функция Func_croatia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2617">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2618">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_croatia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2618">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2649">Номер паспорта гражданина Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2649">Croatia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2650">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2650">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2651">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2651">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2652">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2652">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2653">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2653">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2654">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2654">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2655">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2655">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2656">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2656">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2657">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2657">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2658">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2658">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2659">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2659">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2660">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_eu_passport_date1` ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2660">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2661">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2661">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2662">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2662">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2663">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2663">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Croatia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7d7a729d-32d8-4204-8d01-d5e6a6c25581" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2681">Индивидуальный идентификационный номер (OIB) для Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2681">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2682">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2682">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2683">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2683">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2684">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2684">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2685">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2685">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2686">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2686">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2687">окончательная цифра — это провероальная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2687">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2688">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2688">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2689">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2689">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2690">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2690">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2691">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2691">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2692">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2692">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2693">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2693">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2694">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2694">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2695">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2695">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2696">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2696">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2697">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2697">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2728">Номер социального обеспечения хорватии или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2728">Croatia social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2729">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального обеспечения ЕС или типе конфиденциальной информации эквивалентного ИД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2729">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2730">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2730">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2731">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2731">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2732">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2732">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2733">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2733">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2734">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2734">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2735">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2735">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2736">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2736">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2737">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2737">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2738">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2738">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2739">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2739">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2740">Функция находит  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2740">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2741">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2741">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2742">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2742">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2743">Функция находит  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2743">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2744">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2744">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2745">Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2745">Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>
