## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2760">Номер водительского удостоверения для Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2760">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2761">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2761">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2762">12 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2762">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2763">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2763">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2764">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2764">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2765">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2765">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2766">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2766">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2767">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2767">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2768">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2768">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2769">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2769">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2770">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2770">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="356fa104-f9ac-4aff-a0e4-2e6e65ea06c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2895">Удостоверение личности для Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2895">Cyprus identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2896">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2896">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2897">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2897">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2898">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2898">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2899">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2899">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2900">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2900">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2901">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2901">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2902">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2902">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2903">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2903">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2904">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2904">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2905">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2905">10 digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2906">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2906">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2907">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2907">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2908">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2908">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2909">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2909">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2910">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2910">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2911">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2911">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2912">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2912">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2913">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2913">Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2914">id card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2914">id card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2915">номер удостоверения личности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2915">identity card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2916">kim kimti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2916">kimlik karti</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2917">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2917">national identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2918">личный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2918">personal id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2919">ταυτοτητασ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2919">ταυτοτητασ</span></span>


## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2920">Номер паспорта гражданина Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2920">Cyprus passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2921">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2921">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2922">одна буква, за которой следуют 6–8 цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2922">one letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2923">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2923">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2924">одна буква, за которой следуют от шести до восьми цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2924">one letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2925">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2925">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2926">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2926">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2927">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2927">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2928">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2928">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2929">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2929">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2930">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2930">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2931">Регулярное выражение `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` находит дату в формате ДД/ММ/YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2931">The regular expression `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD/MM/YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2932">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2932">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2933">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2933">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2934">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2934">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>  
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="9193e2e8-7f8c-43c1-a274-ac40d651936f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2935">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2935">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2963">Идентификационный номер налога на Кипре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2963">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2964">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2964">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2965">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2965">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2966">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2966">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2967">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2967">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2968">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2968">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2969">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2969">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2970">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2970">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2971">восемь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2971">eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2972">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2972">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2973">восемь цифр и одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2973">eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2974">"0" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2974">a "0" or "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2975">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2975">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2976">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2976">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2977">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2977">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2978">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2978">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2979">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2979">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2980">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2980">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2981">Функция находит  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2981">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2982">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2982">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2983">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2983">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-2984">Функция находит  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-2984">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="40e64bd9-55f3-4a09-9bd6-1db18dced9dd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3012">Номер водительского удостоверения для Чешский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3012">Czech driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3013">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3013">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3014">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3014">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3015">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3015">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3016">восемь букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3016">eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3017">буква "E" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3017">letter 'E' (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3018">буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3018">a letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3019">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3019">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3020">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3020">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3021">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3021">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3022">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3022">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3023">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3023">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3024">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3024">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3025">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3025">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3026">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3026">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <Entity id="86b40d3b-d8ea-4c36-aab0-ef9416a6769c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3152">Номер паспорта гражданина Чешский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3152">Czech passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3153">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3153">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3154">восемь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3154">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3155">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3155">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3156">восемь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3156">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3157">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3157">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3158">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3158">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3159">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3159">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3160">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3160">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3161">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3161">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3162">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3162">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3163">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_eu_passport_date1` ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3163">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3164">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3164">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3165">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3165">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3166">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3166">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Czech Republic Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7bcd8ce8-5e92-4bbe-bc92-fa669f0369fa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3188">Номер личного удостоверения для чешских пользователей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3188">Czech personal identity number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3189">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3189">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3190">девять цифр с необязательной косой чертой (старый формат) 10 цифр с необязательной косой чертой (новый формат)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3190">nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) 10 digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3191">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3191">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3192">девять цифр (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3192">nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3193">шесть цифр, которые представляют дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3193">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3194">необязательная косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3194">an optional forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3195">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3195">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3196">10 цифр (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3196">10 digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3197">шесть цифр, которые представляют дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3197">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3198">необязательная косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3198">an optional forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3199">четыре цифры, где последняя цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3199">four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3200">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3200">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3201">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3201">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3202">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3202">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3203">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3203">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3204">функция Func_czech_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3204">The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3205">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_czech_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3205">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3206">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3206">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3207">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3207">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3208">Функция Func_czech_id_card_new_format находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3208">The function Func_czech_id_card_new_format finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3209">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3209">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3000.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card_new_format" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3256">Номер социального обеспечения для Чешский или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3256">Czech social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3257">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального обеспечения ЕС или типе конфиденциальной информации эквивалентного ИД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3257">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3258">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3258">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3259">10 цифр и знаки задней знаки в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3259">10 digits and a backslash in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3260">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3260">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3261">10 цифр и ответная знаки:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3261">10 digits and a backslash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3262">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3262">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD):</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3263">замещенная на задний ряд</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3263">a backslash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3264">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру, отделяя людей от одной и той же даты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3264">three digits that correspond to a serial number that separates persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3265">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3265">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3266">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3266">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3267">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3267">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3268">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3268">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3269">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3269">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3270">Функция находит  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3270">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3271">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3271">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3272">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3272">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3273">Функция находит  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3273">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3289">Номер водительского удостоверения для Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3289">Denmark driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3290">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3290">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3291">восемь цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3291">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3292">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3292">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3293">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3293">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3294">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3294">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3295">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3295">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3296">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3296">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3297">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3297">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3298">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3298">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3299">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3299">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="98a95812-6203-451a-a220-d39870ebef0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3300">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3300">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3301">Keywords_eu_driver s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3301">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

## <a name="denmark-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3423">Номер паспорта гражданина Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3423">Denmark passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3424">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3424">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3425">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3425">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3426">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3426">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3427">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3427">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3428">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3428">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3429">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3429">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3430">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3430">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3431">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3431">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3432">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3432">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3433">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3433">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3434">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date2` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3434">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3435">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3435">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3436">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3436">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3437">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3437">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="25e8c47e-e6fe-4884-a211-74898f8c0196" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="denmark-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3457">Персональный идентификационный номер для Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3457">Denmark personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3458">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3458">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3459">10 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3459">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3460">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3460">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3461">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3461">10 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3462">шесть цифр в формате ДДММАЙ, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3462">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3463">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3463">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3464">четыре цифры, где последняя цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3464">four digits where the final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3465">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3465">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3466">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3466">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3467">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3467">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3468">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3468">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3469">Регулярное выражение Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3469">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3470">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_denmark_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3470">A keyword from Keyword_denmark_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3471">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3471">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3472">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3472">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3473">Регулярное выражение Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3473">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3474">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3474">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="6c4f2fef-56e1-4c00-8093-88d7a01cf460" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_denmark_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3541">sygesikringskort</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3541">sygesikringskort</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3542">sygesikringskortnr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3542">sygesikringskortnr</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3543">sygesikringskortnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3543">sygesikringskortnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3544">sygesikringsnr</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3544">sygesikringsnr</span></span>

## <a name="denmark-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3546">Номер социального обеспечения для Дании или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3546">Denmark social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3547">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только для номера социального обеспечения ЕС или типа конфиденциальной информации эквивалентного ИД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3547">This sensitive information type entity is only available the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3548">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3548">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3549">10 цифр и дефис в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3549">10 digits and a hyphen in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3550">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3550">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3551">10 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3551">10 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3552">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3552">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3553">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3553">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3554">четыре цифры, соответствующие последовательному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3554">four digits that correspond to a sequence number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3555">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3555">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3556">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3556">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3557">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3557">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3558">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3558">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3559">Функция находит  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3559">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3560">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3560">A keyword from  `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3561">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3561">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3562">Функция находит  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3562">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3563">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3563">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3564">Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3564">Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3565">персональный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3565">personal identification number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3567">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3567">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3568">nationalnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3568">nationalnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3569">ssn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3569">ssn#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3573">personalidnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3573">personalidnumber#</span></span>

## <a name="drug-enforcement-agency-dea-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3576">Номер агентства по правоохранительным органам (DEA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3576">Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3577">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3577">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3578">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3578">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3579">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3579">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3580">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3580">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3581">одна буква (без регистра) из этого набора возможных букв: abcdefghjklmnprstux, который является регистратором кода</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3581">one letter (not case-sensitive) from this set of possible letters: abcdefghjklmnprstux, which is a registrant code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3582">одна буква (без регистра), которая является первой буквой фамилии регистратора или цифрой "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3582">one letter (not case-sensitive), which is the first letter of the registrant's last name or digit '9'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3583">семь цифр, последняя из которых является провероной.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3583">seven digits, the last of which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3584">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3584">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3585">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3585">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3586">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3586">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3587">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3587">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3588">функция Func_dea_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3588">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3589">Найдено ключевое `Keyword_dea_number` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3589">A keyword from `Keyword_dea_number` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3590">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3590">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3591">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3591">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3592">функция Func_dea_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3592">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3593">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3593">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- DEA Number -->
    <Entity id="9a5445ad-406e-43eb-8bd7-cac17ab6d0e4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.1207.000" maxEngineVersion="15.20.3134.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3135.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3594">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3594">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_dea_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3595">Keyword_dea_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3595">Keyword_dea_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3598">администрирование принудительных органы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3598">drug enforcement administration</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3599">агентство по правоохранительным органам</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3599">drug enforcement agency</span></span>


## <a name="estonia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3600">Номер водительского удостоверения для Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3600">Estonia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3601">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3601">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3602">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3602">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3603">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3603">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3604">две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3604">two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3605">буквы "ET" (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3605">the letters "ET" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3606">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3606">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3607">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3607">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3608">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3608">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3609">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3609">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3610">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3610">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3611">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3611">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3612">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3612">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="51da8171-da70-4cc1-9d65-055a59ca4f83" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3631">driverslicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3631">driverslicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3632">driverslicenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3632">driverslicenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3633">drivers lic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3633">drivers lic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3634">drivers lics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3634">drivers lics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3635">drivers license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3635">drivers license</span></span>

## <a name="estonia-personal-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3738">Персональный идентификационный код Для Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3738">Estonia Personal Identification Code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3739">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3739">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3740">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3740">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3741">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3741">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3742">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3742">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3743">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3743">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3744">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3744">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3745">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3745">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3746">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3746">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3747">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3747">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3748">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3748">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3749">одна цифра, соответствующая полу и минуте рождения (нечетное число самца, четное число самка; 1-2: 19-й год; 3-4: 20-й год; 5-6: 21-й год)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3749">one digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3750">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3750">six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3751">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру, отделяющие пользователей от одной и той же даты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3751">three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3752">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3752">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3753">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3753">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3754">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3754">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3755">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3755">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3756">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3756">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3757">Функция находит  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3757">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3758">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3758">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3759">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3759">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3760">Функция находит  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3760">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Personal Identification Code -->
      <Entity id="bfb26de6-dad5-4d48-ab72-4789cdd0654c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">

          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3793">Номер паспорта гражданина Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3793">Estonia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3794">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3794">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3795">одна буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3795">one letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3796">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3796">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3797">одна буква, за которой следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3797">one letter followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3798">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3798">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3799">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3799">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3800">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3800">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3801">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3801">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3802">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3802">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3803">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3803">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3804">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_eu_passport_date1` ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3804">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3805">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3805">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3806">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3806">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3807">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3807">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61f7073a-509e-425b-a754-bc01bb5d5b8c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3825">Номер банковской карты для ЕС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3825">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3826">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3826">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3827">16 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3827">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3828">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3828">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3829">Сложный и надежный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3829">Complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3830">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3830">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3831">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3831">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3832">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3832">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3833">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3833">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3834">Функция Func_eu_debit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3834">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3835">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3835">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3836">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_eu_debit_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3836">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3837">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3837">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3838">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_security_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3838">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3839">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3839">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3840">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3840">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-3841">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-3841">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
