## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4288">Номер водительского удостоверения для Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4288">Finland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4289">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4289">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4290">10 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4290">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4291">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4291">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4292">10 цифр, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4292">10 digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4293">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4293">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4294">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4294">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4295">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4295">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4296">цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4296">a digit or letter</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4297">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4297">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4298">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4298">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4299">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4299">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4300">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4300">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4301">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4301">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4302">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4302">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Finland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="bb3b27a3-79bd-4ac4-81a7-f9fca3c7d1a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4303">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4303">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="finland-european-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4433">Номер медицинского страхования для Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4433">Finland european health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4434">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4434">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4435">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4435">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4436">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4436">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4437">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4437">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4438">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4438">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4439">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4439">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4440">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4440">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4441">20-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4441">20-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4442">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4442">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4443">20-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4443">20-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4444">10 цифр — 8024680246</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4444">10 digits - 8024680246</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4445">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4445">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4446">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4446">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4447">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4447">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4448">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4448">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4449">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4449">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4450">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4450">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4451">Regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4451">The regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4452">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4452">A keyword from Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland European Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="60f75aed-81bf-4625-89b0-0846b9248ee7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4470">Национальный ИД Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4470">Finland national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4471">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4471">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4472">шесть цифр плюс символ, указывающий на время года, плюс три цифры плюс провероная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4472">six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4473">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4473">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4474">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4474">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4475">шесть цифр в формате ДДММАЙ, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4475">six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are a date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4476">маркер "-", "+" или "a"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4476">century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4477">трехзначный персональный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4477">three-digit personal identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4478">цифра или буква (без чувствительность к делу), которая является проверокой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4478">a digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4479">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4479">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4480">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4480">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4481">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4481">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4482">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4482">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4483">функция Func_finnish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4483">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4484">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_finnish_national_id,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4484">a keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4485">контрольнаяума передается</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4485">the checksum passes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4486">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4486">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4487">функция Func_finnish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4487">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4488">контрольнаяума передается</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4488">the checksum passes</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finnish National ID-->
      <Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4537">Номер паспорта гражданина Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4537">Finland passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4538">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4538">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4539">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4539">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4540">сочетание девяти букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4540">combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4541">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4541">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4542">сочетание из девяти букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4542">combination of nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4543">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4543">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4544">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4544">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4545">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4545">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4546">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4546">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4547">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4547">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4548">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4548">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4549">Регулярное выражение `Regex_finland_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4549">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4550">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keyword_finland_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4550">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4551">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_eu_passport_date1` ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4551">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4552">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4552">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4553">Регулярное выражение `Regex_finland_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4553">The regular expression `Regex_finland_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4554">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keyword_finland_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4554">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_finland_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_finland_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4567">Keyword_finland_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4567">Keyword_finland_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4578">Номер водительского удостоверения для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4578">France driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4579">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4579">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4580">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4580">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4581">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4581">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4582">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4582">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4583">12 цифр с проверкой подлинности, чтобы избежать путаницы с похожими шаблонами, например французскими номерами телефонов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4583">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4584">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4584">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4585">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4585">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4586">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4586">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4587">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4587">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4588">функция Func_french_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4588">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4589">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_french_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4589">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4716">Номер медицинского страхования для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4716">France health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4717">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4717">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4718">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4718">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4719">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4719">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4720">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4720">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4721">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4721">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4722">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4722">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4723">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4723">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4724">21-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4724">21-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4725">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4725">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4726">21-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4726">21-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4727">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4727">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4728">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4728">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4729">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4729">10 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4730">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4730">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4731">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4731">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4732">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4732">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4733">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4733">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4734">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4734">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4735">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4735">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4736">Regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4736">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4737">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4737">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4738">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4738">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_health_insurance_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4739">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4739">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4740">страховая карта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4740">insurance card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4741">carte vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4741">carte vitale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4742">carte d'assuré social</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4742">carte d'assuré social</span></span>


## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4743">Национальный удостоверение личности для Франции (CNI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4743">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4744">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4744">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4745">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4745">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4746">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4746">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4747">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4747">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4748">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4748">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4749">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4749">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4750">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4750">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4751">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4751">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4752">регулярное выражение Regex_france_cni находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4752">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4753">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4753">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4754">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4754">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4758">carte nationale d'idenite no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4758">carte nationale d'idenite no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4759">cni #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4759">cni#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4760">cni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4760">cni</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4761">compte bancaire</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4761">compte bancaire</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4762">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4762">national identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4763">national identity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4763">national identity</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4764">nationalidno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4764">nationalidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4765">numéro d'assurance maladie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4765">numéro d'assurance maladie</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4766">numéro de carte vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4766">numéro de carte vitale</span></span>

   
## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4767">Номер паспорта гражданина Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4767">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4768">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4768">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4769">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4769">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4770">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4770">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4771">девять цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4771">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4772">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4772">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4773">девять цифр и букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4773">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4774">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4774">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4775">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4775">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4776">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4776">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4777">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4777">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4778">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4778">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4779">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4779">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4780">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4780">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4781">Функция находит `Func_fr_passport` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4781">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4782">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4782">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4783">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4783">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4784">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4784">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4785">Функция находит `Func_fr_passport` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4785">The function `Func_fr_passport` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4786">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4786">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_france_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- France Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4787">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4787">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4793">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4793">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4794">passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4794">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4795">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4795">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4796">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4796">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4797">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4797">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4798">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4798">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4799">Keywords_france_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4799">Keywords_france_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4800">numéro de passeport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4800">numéro de passeport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4801">passeport n °</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4801">passeport n °</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4802">passeport non</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4802">passeport non</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4803">passeport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4803">passeport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4804">passeport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4804">passeport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4805">passeportnon</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4805">passeportnon</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4806">passeportn °</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4806">passeportn °</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4807">passeportçais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4807">passeport français</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4808">passeport livre</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4808">passeport livre</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4809">passeport carte</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4809">passeport carte</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4810">numéro passeport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4810">numéro passeport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4811">passeport n°</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4811">passeport n°</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4812">n° du passeport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4812">n° du passeport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4813">n° passeport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4813">n° passeport</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_date"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4814">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4814">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4815">дата проблемы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4815">date of issue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4816">дата окончания срока действия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4816">date of expiry</span></span>


## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4817">Номер социального обеспечения для Франции (INSEE) или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4817">France social security number (INSEE) or equivalent identification</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4818">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4818">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4819">15 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4819">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4820">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4820">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4821">Должен соответствовать одному из двух шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4821">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4822">13 цифр, за которыми следуют пробелы, за которыми следуют две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4822">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4823">или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4823">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4824">15 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4824">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4825">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4825">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4826">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4826">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4827">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4827">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4828">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4828">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4829">Функция находит `Func_french_insee` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4829">The function `Func_french_insee` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4830">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4830">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4831">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4831">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4832">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4832">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4833">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4833">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4834">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4834">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France INSEE -->
    <Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4835">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4835">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4865">Идентификационный номер налога для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4865">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4866">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4866">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4867">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4867">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4868">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4868">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4869">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4869">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4870">Одна цифра, которая должна быть 0, 1, 2 или 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4870">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4871">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4871">One digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4872">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4872">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4873">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4873">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4874">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4874">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4875">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4875">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4876">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4876">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4877">три цифры; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4877">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4878">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4878">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4879">Три контрольных цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4879">Three check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4880">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4880">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4881">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4881">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4882">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4882">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4883">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4883">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4884">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4884">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4885">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4885">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4886">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4886">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4887">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4887">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4888">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4888">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4889">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4889">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4890">numéro d'identification fiscale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4890">numéro d'identification fiscale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4891">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4891">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4892">tax identification no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4892">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4893">налоговый идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4893">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4894">tax no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4894">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4895">tax no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4895">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4896">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4896">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4897">налоговый регистрационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4897">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4898">ыd #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4898">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4899">аdno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4899">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4900">ыdnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4900">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4901">taxno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4901">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4902">taxnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4902">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4903">taxnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4903">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4904">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4904">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4905">tin no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4905">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4906">tin #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4906">tin#</span></span>


## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4907">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4907">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4908">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4908">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4909">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4909">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4910">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4910">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4911">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4911">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4912">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4912">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4913">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4913">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4914">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4914">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4915">13 символов букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4915">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4916">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4916">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4917">13 символов букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4917">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4918">две буквы — FR (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4918">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4919">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4919">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4920">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4920">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4921">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4921">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4922">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4922">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4923">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4923">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4924">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4924">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4925">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4925">an optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4926">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4926">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4927">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4927">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4928">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4928">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4929">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4929">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4930">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4930">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4931">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4931">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4932">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4932">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4933">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4933">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4934">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4934">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4935">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4935">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4942">taxe valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4942">taxe valeur ajoutée</span></span>

## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4947">Номер водительского удостоверения для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4947">Germany driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4948">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ДЛЯ ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4948">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4949">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4949">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4950">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4950">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4951">сочетание 11 цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4951">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4952">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4952">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4953">11 цифр и букв (без чувствительность к буквам):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4953">11 digits and letters (not case-sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4954">цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4954">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4955">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4955">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4956">шесть цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4956">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4957">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4957">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4958">цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4958">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4959">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4959">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4960">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4960">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4961">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4961">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4962">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4962">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4963">Функция Func_german_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4963">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4964">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4964">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-4965">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-4965">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5114">Номер удостоверения личности для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5114">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5115">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5115">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5116">с 1 ноября 2010 г.: девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5116">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5117">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.: 10 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5117">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5118">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5118">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5119">с 1 ноября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5119">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5120">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5120">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5121">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5121">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5122">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5122">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5123">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5123">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5124">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5124">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5125">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5125">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5126">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5126">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5127">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5127">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5128">регулярное выражение Regex_germany_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5128">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5129">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_germany_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5129">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5130">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5130">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5131">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5131">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5132">ausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5132">ausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5133">gpid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5133">gpid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5134">identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5134">identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5135">identifikation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5135">identifikation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5136">identifizierungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5136">identifizierungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5137">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5137">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5138">идентификациный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5138">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5139">id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5139">id-nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5140">личный ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5140">personal id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5141">personalausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5141">personalausweis</span></span>

## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5145">Номер паспорта гражданина Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5145">Germany passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5146">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5146">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5147">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5147">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5148">10 цифр или букв.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5148">10 digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5149">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5149">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5150">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5150">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5151">первый символ — это цифра или буква из этого набора (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5151">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5152">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5152">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5153">пять цифр или букв из этого набора (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5153">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5154">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5154">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5155">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5155">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5156">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5156">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5157">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5157">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5158">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5158">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5159">функция Func_german_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5159">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5160">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из или `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5160">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5161">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5161">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5162">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5162">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5163">функция Func_german_passport_data находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5163">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5164">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из или `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5164">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5165">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5165">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5188">Идентификационный номер налога для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5188">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5189">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5189">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5190">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5190">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5191">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5191">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5192">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5192">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5193">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5193">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5194">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5194">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5195">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5195">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5196">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5196">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5197">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5197">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5198">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5198">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5199">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5199">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5200">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5200">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5201">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5201">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5202">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5202">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5203">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5203">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5204">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5204">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5205">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5205">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5206">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5206">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5207">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5207">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5208">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5208">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5209">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5209">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5210">Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5210">Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5211">identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5211">identifikationsnummer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5214">steuernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5214">steuernummer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5217">налоговый идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5217">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5218">tax no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5218">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5219">tax no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5219">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5220">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5220">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5221">налоговый регистрационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5221">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5222">ыd #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5222">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5223">аdno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5223">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5224">ыdnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5224">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5225">taxno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5225">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5226">taxnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5226">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5227">taxnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5227">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5228">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5228">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5229">tin no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5229">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5230">tin #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5230">tin#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5231">zinn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5231">zinn#</span></span>
