- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5233">zinnnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5233">zinnnummer</span></span>


## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5234">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5234">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5235">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5235">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5236">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5236">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5237">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5237">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5238">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5238">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5239">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5239">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5240">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5240">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5241">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5241">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5242">11 символов букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5242">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5243">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5243">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5244">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5244">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5245">буква D или d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5245">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5246">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5246">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5247">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5247">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5248">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5248">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5249">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5249">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5250">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5250">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5251">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5251">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5252">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5252">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5253">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5253">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5254">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5254">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5255">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5255">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5256">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5256">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5257">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5257">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5258">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5258">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5259">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5259">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5260">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5260">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5269">mehrwertsteuer nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5269">mehrwertsteuer nummer</span></span>


## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5270">Номер водительского удостоверения для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5270">Greece driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5271">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5271">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5272">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5272">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5273">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5273">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5274">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5274">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5275">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5275">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5276">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5276">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5277">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5277">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5278">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5278">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5279">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5279">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5280">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5280">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5281">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5281">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5407">Карточка национального удостоверения личности для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5407">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5408">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5408">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5409">Сочетание 7–8 букв и чисел, а также тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5409">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5410">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5410">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5411">Семь букв и чисел (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5411">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5412">одна буква (любая буква греческого алфавита);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5412">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5413">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5413">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5414">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5414">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5415">Восемь букв и чисел (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5415">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5416">две буквы, которые в прописном виде есть как в греческом, так и латинском алфавите (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5416">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5417">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5417">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5418">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5418">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5419">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5419">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5420">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5420">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5421">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5421">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5422">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5422">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5423">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5423">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5424">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_greece_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5424">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5425">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5425">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5426">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5426">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5427">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5427">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5428">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5428">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5429">греческий ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5429">greek id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5430">греческий национальный ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5430">greek national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5431">греческий персональный id-карта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5431">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5432">греческий ид полиции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5432">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5433">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5433">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5434">tautotita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5434">tautotita</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5435">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5435">ταυτότητα</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5436">ταυτότητας</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5436">ταυτότητας</span></span>


## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5437">Номер паспорта гражданина Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5437">Greece passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5438">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5438">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5439">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5439">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5440">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5440">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5441">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5441">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5442">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5442">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5443">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5443">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5444">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5444">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5445">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5445">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5446">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5446">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5447">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5447">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5448">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM YY (пример — 28 августа 19) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5448">The regular expression `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM YY (Example - 28 Aug 19) or a keyword from `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5449">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5449">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5450">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5450">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5451">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5451">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7e65eb47-cdf9-4f52-8f90-2a27d5ee67e3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5452">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5452">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5462">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5462">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5463">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5463">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5464">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5464">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5465">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5465">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5466">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5466">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5467">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5467">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span></span>


## <a name="greece-social-security-number-amka"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5468">Номер социального обеспечения для Греция (AMKA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5468">Greece Social Security Number (AMKA)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5469">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5469">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5470">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5470">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5471">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5471">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5472">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5472">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5473">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5473">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5474">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5474">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5475">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5475">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5476">Одиннадцати цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5476">Eleven digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5477">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5477">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5478">6 цифр в качестве даты рождения YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5478">6 digits as date of birth YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5479">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5479">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5480">проверяемая цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5480">a check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5481">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5481">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5482">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5482">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5483">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5483">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5484">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5484">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5485">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5485">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5486">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5486">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5487">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5487">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5488">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5488">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Greece Social Security Number (AMKA) -->
      <Entity id="e39b03f4-50ea-41ae-af7a-a4b9539596ad" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5489">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5489">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5490">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5490">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5491">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5491">ssn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5492">ssn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5492">ssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5493">social security no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5493">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5494">socialsecurityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5494">socialsecurityno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5495">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5495">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5496">amka</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5496">amka</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5497">a.m.k.a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5497">a.m.k.a.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5498">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5498">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span></span>


## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5499">Идентификационный номер налога для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5499">Greece tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5500">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5500">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5501">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5501">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5502">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5502">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5503">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5503">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5504">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5504">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5505">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5505">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5506">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5506">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5507">Девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5507">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5508">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5508">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5509">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5509">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5510">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5510">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5511">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5511">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5512">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5512">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5513">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5513">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5514">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5514">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5515">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5515">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5544">Номер удостоверения личности в Гонконге (HKID)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5544">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5545">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5545">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5546">Сочетание 8–9 букв и чисел, а также необязательные скобки вокруг последнего символа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5546">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5547">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5547">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5548">Сочетание 8–9 букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5548">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5549">1–2 буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5549">1-2 letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5550">шесть цифр; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5550">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5551">последний символ (любая цифра или буква "A") является проверочной цифрой и заключен в скобки (необязательно).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5551">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5552">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5552">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5553">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5553">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5554">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5554">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5555">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5555">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5556">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5556">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5557">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_hong_kong_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5557">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5558">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5558">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5559">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5559">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5560">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5560">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5561">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5561">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5562">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5562">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_hong_kong_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5563">Keyword_hong_kong_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5563">Keyword_hong_kong_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5564">hkid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5564">hkid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5565">удостоверение личности в Гонконге</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5565">hong kong identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5566">HKIDC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5566">HKIDC</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5567">id card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5567">id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5568">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5568">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5569">удостоверение hk</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5569">hk identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5570">hong kong id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5570">hong kong id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5571">香港身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5571">香港身份證</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5601">Номер водительского удостоверения для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5601">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5602">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5602">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5603">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5603">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5604">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5604">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5605">Две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5605">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5606">Две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5606">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5607">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5607">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5608">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5608">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5609">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5609">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5610">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5610">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5611">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5611">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5612">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5612">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5613">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5613">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <Entity id="9d31c46b-6e6b-444c-aeb1-6dd7e604bb24" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5738">Персональный идентификационный номер для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5738">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5739">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5739">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5740">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5740">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5741">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5741">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5742">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5742">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5743">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5743">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5744">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5744">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5745">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5745">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5746">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5746">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5747">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5747">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5748">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5748">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5749">Одна цифра, соответствующая полу (1- и 2-женская, другая цифра также возможна для граждан, которые раньше 1900 г., или граждан с двойным паспортом)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5749">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5750">Шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5750">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5751">Три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5751">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5752">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5752">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5753">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5753">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5754">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5754">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5755">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5755">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5756">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5756">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5757">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5757">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5758">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5758">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5759">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5759">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5760">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5760">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5761">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5761">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5762">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5762">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5763">id number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5763">id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5764">identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5764">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5765">sz ig</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5765">sz ig</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5766">sz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5766">sz.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5767">ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5767">ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5768">sz.ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5768">sz.ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5769">személyazonosító igazolvány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5769">személyazonosító igazolvány</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5770">személyi igazolvány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5770">személyi igazolvány</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5771">Номер паспорта гражданина Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5771">Hungary passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5772">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5772">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5773">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5773">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5774">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5774">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5775">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5775">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5776">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5776">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5777">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5777">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5778">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5778">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5779">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5779">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5780">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5780">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5781">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5781">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5782">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM YY (пример — 01 MÁR/MAR 12) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5782">The regular expression `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YY (Example - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5783">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5783">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5784">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5784">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5785">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5785">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5b483910-9aa7-4c99-9917-f4001464bda7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5786">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5786">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5787">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5787">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-taj"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5805">Номер социального обеспечения для Венгрии (TAJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5805">Hungary social security number (TAJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5806">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5806">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5807">Девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5807">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5808">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5808">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5809">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5809">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5810">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5810">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5811">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5811">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5812">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5812">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5813">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5813">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5814">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5814">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5815">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5815">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5816">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5816">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5817">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5817">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Social Security Number (TAJ) -->
      <Entity id="0de78315-9537-47f5-95ab-b3e77eba3993" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5837">Идентификационный номер налога для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5837">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5838">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5838">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5839">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5839">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5840">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5840">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5841">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5841">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5842">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5842">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5843">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5843">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5844">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5844">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5845">10 цифр без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5845">10 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5846">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5846">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5847">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5847">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5848">Одна цифра, которая должна быть "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5848">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5849">восемь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5849">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5850">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5850">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5851">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5851">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5852">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5852">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5853">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5853">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5854">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5854">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5855">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5855">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5856">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5856">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5857">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5857">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5858">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5858">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
