## <a name="hungary-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5884">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5884">Hungary value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5885">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5885">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5886">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5886">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5887">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5887">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5888">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5888">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5889">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5889">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5890">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5890">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5891">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5891">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5892">10 символов букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5892">10 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5893">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5893">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5894">10 символов букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5894">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5895">две буквы — HU или hu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5895">two letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5896">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5896">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5897">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5897">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5898">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5898">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5899">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5899">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5900">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5900">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5901">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5901">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5902">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5902">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5903">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5903">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5904">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5904">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5905">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5905">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5906">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5906">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_hungary_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5907">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5907">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5908">vat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5908">vat</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5909">номер налога на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5909">value added tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5910">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5910">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5911">vatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5911">vatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5912">hungarianvatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5912">hungarianvatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5913">tax no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5913">tax no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5914">налог на добавленную стоимость ( áfa)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5914">value added tax áfa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5915">közösségi adószám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5915">közösségi adószám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5916">általános forgalmi adó szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5916">általános forgalmi adó szám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5917">hozzáadottérték adó</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5917">hozzáadottérték adó</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5918">áfa szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5918">áfa szám</span></span>


## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5919">Постоянный номер учетной записи Для Индии (PAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5919">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5920">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5920">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5921">10 букв или цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5921">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5922">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5922">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5923">10 букв или цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5923">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5924">Три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5924">Three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5925">Буква в C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5925">A letter in C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5926">Буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5926">A letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5927">Четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5927">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5928">Буква, которая является алфавитной провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5928">A letter that is an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5929">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5929">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5930">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5930">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5931">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5931">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5932">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5932">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5933">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5933">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5934">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_permanent_account_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5934">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5935">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5935">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5936">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5936">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
      <Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3520.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5937">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5937">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_india_permanent_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5938">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5938">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5939">Permanent Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5939">Permanent Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5940">PAN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5940">PAN</span></span> 
   
## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5941">Уникальный идентификационный номер (Aadhaar) для Индии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5941">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5942">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5942">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5943">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы или тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5943">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5944">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5944">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5945">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5945">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5946">Цифра, которая не является 0 или 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5946">A digit which is not 0 or 1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5947">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5947">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5948">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5948">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5949">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5949">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5950">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5950">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5951">Последняя цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5951">The final digit, which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5952">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5952">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5953">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5953">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5954">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5954">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5955">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5955">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5956">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5956">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5957">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_aadhar;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5957">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5958">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5958">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- 
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5959">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5959">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5960">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5960">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5961">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5961">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5962">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5962">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_india_aadhar"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5963">Keyword_india_aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5963">Keyword_india_aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5964">aadhaar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5964">aadhaar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5965">aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5965">aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5966">aadhar #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5966">aadhar#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5967">uid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5967">uid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5968">आधार</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5968">आधार</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5969">uidai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5969">uidai</span></span>
   
## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5970">Номер удостоверения личности (KTP) для Индонезии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5970">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5971">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5971">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5972">16 цифр, содержащих необязательные точки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5972">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5973">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5973">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5974">16 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5974">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5975">две цифры (код провинции);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5975">Two-digit province code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5976">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5976">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5977">две цифры (код округа или города);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5977">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5978">две цифры (код района);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5978">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5979">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5979">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5980">Шесть цифр в формате ДДММАЙ, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5980">Six digits in the format DDMMYY, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5981">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5981">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5982">четыре цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5982">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5983">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5983">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5984">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5984">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5985">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5985">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5986">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5986">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5987">регулярное выражение Regex_indonesia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5987">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5988">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_indonesia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5988">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5994">Международный номер банковского счета (IBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5994">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5995">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5995">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5996">Код страны (две буквы), а также проверочные цифры (две) и номер bban (до 30 символов)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5996">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5997">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5997">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5998">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5998">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-5999">Двухбуквенный код страны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-5999">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6000">Две проверочные цифры (после которых может следовать пробел) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6000">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6001">1–7 групп из четырех букв или цифр (могут разделяться пробелами)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6001">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6002">1–3 буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6002">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-p137">Формат для названия каждой из стран немного отличается. Тип конфиденциальной информации IBAN применяется к следующим 60 странам:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-p137">The format for each country is slightly different. The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6005">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6005">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6006">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6006">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6007">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6007">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6008">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6008">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6009">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6009">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6010">функция Func_iban находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6010">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6011">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6011">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6012">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6012">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6013">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6013">None</span></span>

   
## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-10-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6014">Международная классификация болезни (ICD-10-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6014">International classification of diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6015">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6015">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6016">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6016">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6017">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6017">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6018">Ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6018">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6019">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6019">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6020">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6020">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6021">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6021">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6022">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6022">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6023">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6023">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6024">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6024">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6025">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6025">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6026">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_, обновленное.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6026">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6027">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6027">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6028">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_10_updated ключевых слов, который основан на международной классификации "Болезни", "Десятая редакция", "Модификация" [(ICD-10-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6028">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6029">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не страховые коды.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6029">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6030">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_10_codes ключевых слов, который основан на международной классификации "Болезни", "Десятая редакция", "Модификация" [(ICD-10-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6030">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6031">Этот тип ищет только страховые коды, а не описание.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6031">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-9-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6032">Международная классификация болезни (ICD-9-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6032">International classification of diseases (ICD-9-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6033">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6033">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6034">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6034">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6035">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6035">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6036">Ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6036">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6037">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6037">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6038">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6038">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6039">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6039">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6040">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6040">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6041">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6041">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6042">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6042">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6043">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6043">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6044">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6044">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <Entity id="fa3f9c74-ee07-4c52-b5f2-085d6b2c0ec4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6045">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6045">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6046">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_updated ключевых слов, который основан на международной классификации", "Девятая редакция", "Модификация" [(ICD-9-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6046">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6047">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не страховые коды.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6047">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6048">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_codes ключевых слов, который основан на международной классификации "Болезни", "Девятая редакция", "Модификация" [(ICD-9-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6048">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6049">Этот тип ищет только страховые коды, а не описание.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6049">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6050">IP-адрес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6050">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6051">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6051">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6052">IPv4:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6052">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6053">Сложный шаблон, учитывая форматированные (периоды) и неформатированные (без периодов) версии IPv4-адресов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6053">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6054">IPv6:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6054">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6055">Сложный шаблон, который учитывает форматированные номера IPv6 (включая двоеточия)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6055">Complex pattern that accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6056">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6056">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6057">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6057">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6058">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6058">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6059">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6059">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6060">Для IPv6 политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6060">For IPv6, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6061">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6061">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6062">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6062">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6063">В случае с протоколом IPv4 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6063">For IPv4, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6064">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv4_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6064">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6065">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6065">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6066">В случае с протоколом IPv6 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6066">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6067">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6067">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6068">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6068">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6071">IP-адрес (это ключевое слово с чувствительностью к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6071">IP (this keyword is case-sensitive)</span></span>

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6076">Номер водительского удостоверения для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6076">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6077">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6077">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6078">Шесть цифр, за которыми следуют четыре буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6078">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6079">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6079">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6080">Шесть цифр и четыре буквы:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6080">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6081">Шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6081">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6082">Четыре буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6082">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6083">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6083">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6084">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6084">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6085">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6085">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6086">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6086">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6087">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6087">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6088">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6088">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="e01bccd9-eb4d-414f-ace1-e9b6a4c4a2ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6212">Номер паспорта гражданина Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6212">Ireland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6213">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6213">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6214">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6214">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6215">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6215">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6216">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6216">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6217">Две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6217">Two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6218">семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6218">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6219">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6219">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6220">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6220">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6221">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6221">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6222">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6222">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6223">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6223">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6224">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6224">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6225">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM ГГ ГГ (пример — 01 BEA/MAY 1988) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6225">The regular expression `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6226">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6226">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6227">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6227">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6228">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6228">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="a2130f27-9ee2-4103-84f9-a6b1ee7d0cbf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6252">Номер личной службы (PPS) для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6252">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6253">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6253">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6254">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6254">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6255">семь цифр, за которыми следуют 1–2 буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6255">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6256">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6256">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6257">семь цифр, за которыми следуют две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6257">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6258">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6258">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6259">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6259">Old format (until 31 December 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6260">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6260">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6261">от одной до двух букв (без чувствительность к буквам);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6261">one to two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6262">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6262">New format (1 January 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6263">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6263">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6264">буква (без регистрации буквы), которая является алфавитной провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6264">a letter (not case-sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6265">Необязательная буква в диапазоне A-I или W</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6265">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6266">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6266">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6267">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6267">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6268">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6268">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6269">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6269">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6270">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6270">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6271">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6271">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6272">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6272">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6273">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6273">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6274">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6274">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6275">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6275">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6290">ppsno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6290">ppsno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6291">psp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6291">psp</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6292">public service no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6292">public service no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6293">publicserviceno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6293">publicserviceno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6294">publicserviceno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6294">publicserviceno</span></span>

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6320">Номер банковского счета для Израиль</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6320">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6321">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6321">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6322">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6322">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6323">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6323">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6324">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6324">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6325">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6325">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6326">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6326">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6327">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6327">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6328">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6328">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6329">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6329">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6330">Неформатированные:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6330">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6331">	13 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6331">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6332">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6332">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6333">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6333">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6334">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6334">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6335">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6335">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6336">регулярное выражение Regex_israel_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6336">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6337">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_israel_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6337">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6338">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6338">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6339">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6339">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6340">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6340">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6341">Bank Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6341">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6342">Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6342">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6343">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6343">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6344">Национальный идентификационный номер для Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6344">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6345">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6345">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6346">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6346">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6347">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6347">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6348">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6348">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6349">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6349">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6350">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6350">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6351">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6351">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6352">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6352">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6353">функция Func_israeli_national_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6353">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6354">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Israel_National_ID;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6354">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6355">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6355">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

-   <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6361">זהותישר אלית</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6361">זהותישר אלית</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6362">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6362">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6363">هوية إسرائ يلية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6363">هوية إسرائ يلية</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6367">id number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6367">id number</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6371">многоядерный объект</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6371">israeliidentitynumber</span></span>

## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6374">Номер водительского удостоверения для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6374">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6375">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включен в тип конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6375">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6376">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6376">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6377">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6377">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6378">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6378">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6379">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6379">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6380">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6380">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6381">буква "A" или "V" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6381">the letter "A" or "V" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6382">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6382">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6383">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6383">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6384">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6384">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6385">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6385">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6386">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6386">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6387">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6387">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6388">Регулярное выражение `Regex_italy_drivers_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6388">The regular expression `Regex_italy_drivers_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6389">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6389">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
    <Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6516">Финансовый код Для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6516">Italy fiscal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6517">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6517">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6518">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6518">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6519">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6519">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6520">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6520">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6521">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6521">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6522">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6522">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6523">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6523">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6524">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6524">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6525">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6525">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6526">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6526">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6527">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем consonants в имени семейства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6527">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6528">три буквы, соответствующие первому, третьему и четвертому consonants в первом имени</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6528">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6529">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6529">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6530">одна буква, соответствующая букве месяца рождения, — буквы используются в алфавитном порядке, но используются только буквы A к E, H, L, M, P, R to T (таким образом, январь A, а октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6530">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (so, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6531">две цифры, соответствующие дню месяца рождения, чтобы различать полы, 40 добавляется в день рождения для</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6531">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6532">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду региона, определенному для страны, где был человек ( коды для внешних стран)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6532">four digits that correspond to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6533">одна цифра четности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6533">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6534">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6534">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6535">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6535">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6536">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6536">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6537">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6537">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6538">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6538">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6539">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6539">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6540">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6540">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6541">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6541">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6576">Номер паспорта гражданина Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6576">Italy passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6577">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6577">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6578">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6578">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6579">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6579">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6580">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6580">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6581">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6581">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6582">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6582">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6583">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6583">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6584">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6584">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6585">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6585">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6586">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6586">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6587">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6587">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6588">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6588">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6589">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM ГГ ГГ (пример — 01 GEN/JAN 1988) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6589">The regular expression `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6590">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6590">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6591">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6591">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6592">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6592">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="39811019-4750-445f-b26d-4c0e6c431544" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
