## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6616">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6616">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6617">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6617">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6618">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6618">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6619">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6619">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6620">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6620">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6621">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6621">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6622">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6622">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6623">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6623">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6624">13-символьный буквонумерный шаблон с необязательными делетерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6624">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6625">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6625">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6626">13 символов букв и цифр с необязательными разнородных символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6626">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6627">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6627">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6628">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6628">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6629">необязательное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6629">optional space, dot, hyphen, or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6630">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6630">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6631">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6631">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6632">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6632">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6633">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6633">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6634">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6634">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6635">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6635">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6636">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6636">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6637">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6637">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6638">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6638">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6639">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6639">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6640">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6640">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6641">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6641">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6642">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6642">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6643">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6643">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6644">iva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6644">iva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6645">iva #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6645">iva#</span></span>


## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6646">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6646">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6647">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6647">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6648">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6648">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6649">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6649">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6650">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6650">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6651">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6651">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6652">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6652">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6653">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6653">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6654">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6654">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6655">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6655">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6656">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6656">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6657">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6657">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6658">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6658">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6659">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6659">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6660">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6660">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6661">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6661">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6662">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6662">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6663">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6663">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6664">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6664">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6665">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6665">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6666">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6666">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6667">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6667">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6714">Номер водительского удостоверения для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6714">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6715">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6715">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6716">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6716">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6717">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6717">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6718">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6718">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6719">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6719">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6720">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6720">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6721">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6721">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6722">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6722">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6723">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6723">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6724">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6724">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6725">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6725">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6726">Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6726">Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6727">driverlicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6727">driverlicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6728">driverslicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6728">driverslicense</span></span>

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6762">Мой номер для Японии — корпоративный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6762">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6763">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6763">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6764">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6764">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6765">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6765">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6766">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6766">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6767">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6767">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6768">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6768">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6769">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6769">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6770">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6770">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6771">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6771">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6772">13-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6772">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6773">одна цифра от одной до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6773">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6774">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6774">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6775">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6775">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6776">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6776">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6777">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6777">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6778">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6778">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6779">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6779">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6780">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6780">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6781">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6781">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6782">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6782">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6785">корпоративный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6785">corporate number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6789">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6789">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6790">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6790">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6791">個人識別番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6791">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6792">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6792">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6793">法人番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6793">法人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6794">指定通知書</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6794">指定通知書</span></span>


## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6795">Мой номер для Японии — личный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6795">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6797">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6797">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6798">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6798">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6799">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6799">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6800">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6800">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6801">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6801">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6802">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6802">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6803">12-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6803">12-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6804">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6804">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6805">12-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6805">12-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6806">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6806">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6807">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6807">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6808">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6808">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6809">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6809">an optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6810">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6810">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6811">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6811">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6812">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6812">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6813">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6813">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6814">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6814">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6815">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6815">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6816">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6816">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6817">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6817">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6818">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6818">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6831">Номер паспорта гражданина Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6831">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6832">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6832">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6833">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6833">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6834">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6834">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6835">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6835">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6836">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6836">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6837">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6837">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6838">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6838">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6839">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6839">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6840">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6840">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6841">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6841">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6842">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6842">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6843">Keyword_jp_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6843">Keyword_jp_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6844">Passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6844">Passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6845">Passport Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6845">Passport Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6846">Passport No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6846">Passport No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6847">Passport#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6847">Passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6848">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6848">パスポート</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6849">パスポート番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6849">パスポート番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6850">パスポートナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6850">パスポートナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6851">パスポート＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6851">パスポート＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6852">パスポート #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6852">パスポート#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6853">パポ>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6853">パスポートNo.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6854">旅券番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6854">旅券番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6855">旅券番号＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6855">旅券番号＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6856">旅券番号♯</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6856">旅券番号♯</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6857">旅券ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6857">旅券ナンバー</span></span>


## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6858">Номер карты для проживания в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6858">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6859">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6859">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6860">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6860">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6861">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6861">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6862">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6862">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6863">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6863">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6864">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6864">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6865">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6865">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6866">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6866">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6867">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6867">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6868">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6868">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6869">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6869">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6870">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6870">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6871">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6871">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6872">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6872">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6873">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6873">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6874">Номер карты для проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6874">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6875">Карты проживания нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6875">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6876">Карточка для проживания #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6876">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6877">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6877">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6878">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6878">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6879">在留番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6879">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6880">Номер регистрации резидента Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6880">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6881">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6881">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6882">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6882">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6883">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6883">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6884">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6884">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6885">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6885">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6886">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6886">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6887">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6887">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6888">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6888">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6889">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6889">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6890">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6890">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6891">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6891">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6892">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6892">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6893">Resident Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6893">Resident Registration Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6894">Residents Basic Registry Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6894">Residents Basic Registry Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6895">Resident Registration No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6895">Resident Registration No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6896">Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6896">Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6897">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6897">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6898">Basic Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6898">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6899">外国人登録証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6899">外国人登録証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6900">証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6900">証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6901">登録番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6901">登録番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6902">外国人登録証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6902">外国人登録証</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6903">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6903">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6904">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6904">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6905">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6905">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6906">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6906">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6907">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6907">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6908">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6908">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6909">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6909">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6910">шесть цифр ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6910">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6911">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6911">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6912">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6912">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6913">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6913">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6914">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6914">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6915">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6915">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6916">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6916">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6917">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6917">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6918">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6918">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6919">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6919">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6920">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6920">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6921">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6921">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6922">Keyword_jp_sin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6922">Keyword_jp_sin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6923">Social Insurance No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6923">Social Insurance No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6924">Social Insurance Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6924">Social Insurance Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6925">Social Insurance Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6925">Social Insurance Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6926">健康保険被保険者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6926">健康保険被保険者番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6927">健保番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6927">健保番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6928">基礎年金番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6928">基礎年金番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6929">雇用保険被保険者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6929">雇用保険被保険者番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6930">雇用保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6930">雇用保険番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6931">保険証番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6931">保険証番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6932">社会保険番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6932">社会保険番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6933">社会保険No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6933">社会保険No.</span></span>

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6941">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6941">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6942">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6942">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6943">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6943">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6944">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6944">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6945">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6945">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6946">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6946">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6947">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6947">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6948">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6948">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6949">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6949">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6950">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6950">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6951">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6951">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6952">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6952">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-6953">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-6953">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7078">Персональный код для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7078">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7079">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7079">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7080">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7080">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7081">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7081">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7082">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7082">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7083">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7083">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7084">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7084">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7085">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7085">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7086">одна цифра, соответствующая годовщине рождения ("0" для 19-го, "1" для 20-го и "2" для 21-го)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7086">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7087">четыре цифры, генерируемые случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7087">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7088">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7088">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7089">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7089">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7090">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7090">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7091">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7091">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7092">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7092">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7093">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7093">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7094">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7094">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7095">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7095">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7096">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7096">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7097">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7097">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7098">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7098">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7099">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7099">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7162">Номер паспорта гражданина Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7162">Latvia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7163">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7163">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7164">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7164">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7165">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7165">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7166">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7166">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7167">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7167">two digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7168">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7168">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7169">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7169">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7170">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7170">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7171">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7171">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7172">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7172">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7173">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7173">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7174">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7174">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7175">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_eu_passport_date1` ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7175">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7176">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7176">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7177">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7177">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7178">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7178">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="23ae25ec-cc28-421b-b77a-3054eadf1ede" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7201">Номер водительского удостоверения для Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7201">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7202">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7202">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7203">восемь цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7203">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7204">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7204">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7205">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7205">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7206">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7206">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7207">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7207">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7208">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7208">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7209">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7209">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7210">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7210">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7211">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7211">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7336">Персональный код Для Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7336">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7337">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7337">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7338">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7338">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7339">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7339">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7340">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7340">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7341">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7341">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7342">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7342">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7343">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7343">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7344">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7344">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7345">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7345">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7346">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7346">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7347">одна цифра (1–6), соответствующая полу и возрасту человека при рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7347">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7348">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7348">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7349">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7349">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7350">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7350">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7351">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7351">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7352">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7352">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7353">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7353">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7354">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7354">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7355">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7355">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7356">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7356">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7357">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7357">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7358">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7358">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7393">Номер паспорта гражданина Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7393">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7394">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7394">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7395">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7395">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7396">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7396">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7397">восемь цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7397">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7398">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7398">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7399">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7399">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7400">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7400">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7401">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7401">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7402">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7402">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7403">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7403">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7404">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7404">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7405">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7405">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7406">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7406">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7407">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7407">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7427">Номер водительского удостоверения Химмхета</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7427">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7428">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7428">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7429">шесть цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7429">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7430">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7430">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7431">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7431">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7432">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7432">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7433">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7433">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7434">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7434">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7435">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7435">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7436">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7436">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7437">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7437">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7561">Национальный идентификационный номер (естественные лица) для Нюксемнеса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7561">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7562">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7562">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7563">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7563">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7564">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7564">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7565">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7565">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7566">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7566">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7567">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7567">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7568">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7568">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7569">13 цифр без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7569">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7570">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7570">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7571">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7571">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7572">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7572">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7573">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7573">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7574">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7574">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7575">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7575">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7576">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7576">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7577">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7577">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7578">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7578">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7579">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7579">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7580">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7580">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7581">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7581">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
