## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7604">Номер паспорта Химмхета</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7604">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7605">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7605">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7606">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7606">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7607">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7607">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7608">восемь цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7608">eight digits or letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7609">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7609">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7610">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7610">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7611">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7611">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7612">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7612">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7613">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7613">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7614">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7614">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7615">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7615">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7616">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7616">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7617">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7617">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7618">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7618">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="81d5c027-bed9-4421-91a0-3b2e55b3eb85" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7650">Идентификационный номер национального идентификации для Нюмнеса (не является естественным лицом)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7650">Luxemburg national identification number (non-natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7651">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7651">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7652">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7652">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7653">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7653">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7654">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7654">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7655">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7655">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7656">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7656">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7657">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7657">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7658">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7658">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7659">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7659">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7660">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7660">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7661">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7661">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7662">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7662">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7663">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7663">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7664">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7664">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7665">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7665">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7666">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7666">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7667">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7667">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7668">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7668">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7669">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7669">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7670">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7670">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7710">Номер идентификационных карт для Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7710">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7711">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7711">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7712">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7712">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7713">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7713">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7714">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7714">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7715">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7715">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7716">Тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7716">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7717">двух буквный код места рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7717">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7718">Тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7718">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7719">три случайные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7719">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7720">однозначный код пола</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7720">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7721">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7721">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7722">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7722">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7723">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7723">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7724">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7724">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7725">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7725">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7726">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7726">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7753">Номер водительского удостоверения для Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7753">Malta driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7754">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7754">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7755">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7755">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7756">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7756">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7757">сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7757">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7758">два символа (цифры или буквы без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7758">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7759">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7759">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7760">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7760">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7761">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7761">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7762">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7762">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7763">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7763">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7764">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7764">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7765">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7765">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7766">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7766">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7767">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7767">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7768">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7768">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7892">Номер удостоверения личности для Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7892">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7893">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7893">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7894">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7894">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7895">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7895">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7896">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7896">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7897">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7897">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7898">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7898">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7899">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7899">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7900">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7900">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7901">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7901">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7902">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7902">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7903">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7903">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7904">одна буква в "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (без чувствительность к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7904">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7905">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7905">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7906">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7906">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7907">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7907">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7908">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7908">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7909">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7909">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7910">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7910">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7911">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7911">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7912">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7912">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7913">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7913">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7914">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7914">Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7915">citizen service number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7915">citizen service number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7917">identifika numru tal-jett</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7917">identifika numru tal-biljett</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7918">kodiċi numerali personali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7918">kodiċi numerali personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7919">numru ta 'identifzzjoni personali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7919">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7920">numru ta 'identifzzjonident-taxxa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7920">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7921">numru ta 'identifzzjoni uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7921">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7922">numru ta' identità uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7922">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7923">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7923">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7924">numruru-taxxa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7924">numru tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7925">личный числовой код</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7925">personal numeric code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7927">уникальный идентификациный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7927">unique identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7928">uniqueidentityno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7928">uniqueidentityno#</span></span>


## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7929">Номер паспорта гражданина Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7929">Malta passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7930">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7930">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7931">семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7931">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7932">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7932">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7933">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7933">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7934">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7934">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7935">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7935">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7936">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7936">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7937">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7937">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7938">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7938">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7939">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7939">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7940">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_passport_date` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7940">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7941">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7941">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7942">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7942">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7943">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7943">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="b2b21198-48f9-4d13-b2a5-03969bff0fb8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7944">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7944">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7963">Идентификационный номер налога на Мальте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7963">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7964">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7964">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7965">Для граждан Тайваня:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7965">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7966">семь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7966">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7967">Неконвионские граждане и подмайства:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7967">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7968">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7968">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7969">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7969">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7970">Граждане Тайваня: семь цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7970">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7971">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7971">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7972">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7972">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7973">Нефрумовские граждане и сущностями, не относягими к сша: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7973">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7974">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7974">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7975">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7975">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7976">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7976">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7977">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7977">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7978">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7978">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7979">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7979">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7980">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7980">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7981">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7981">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-7982">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-7982">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8015">Номер службы гражданина Нидерландов (BSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8015">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8016">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8016">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8017">восемь или девять цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8017">eight or nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8018">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8018">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8019">восемь-девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8019">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8020">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8020">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8021">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8021">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8022">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8022">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8023">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8023">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8024">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8024">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8025">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8025">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8026">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8026">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8027">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8027">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8028">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8028">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8029">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8029">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8030">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8030">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8031">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8031">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8042">persoonlijk nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8042">persoonlijk nummer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8049">sofinummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8049">sofinummer</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8055">Номер водительского удостоверения для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8055">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8056">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8056">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8057">десять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8057">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8058">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8058">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8059">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8059">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8060">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8060">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8061">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8061">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8062">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8062">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8063">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8063">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8064">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8064">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8065">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8065">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8193">Номер паспорта гражданина Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8193">Netherlands passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8194">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8194">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8195">девять букв или цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8195">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8196">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8196">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8197">девять букв или цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8197">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8198">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8198">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8199">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8199">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8200">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8200">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8201">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8201">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8202">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8202">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8203">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8203">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8204">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM YYYY (пример — 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8204">The regular expression `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8205">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8205">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8206">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8206">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8207">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8207">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61786727-bafd-45f6-94d9-888d815e228e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8220">Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8220">Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8221">paspoort nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8221">paspoort nummer</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8225">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8225">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8226">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8226">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8227">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8227">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8228">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8228">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8229">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8229">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8230">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8230">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8231">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8231">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8232">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8232">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8233">девять цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8233">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8234">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8234">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8235">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8235">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8236">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8236">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8237">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8237">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8238">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8238">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8239">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8239">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8240">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8240">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8241">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8241">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8242">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8242">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8243">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8243">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8281">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8281">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8282">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8282">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8283">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8283">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8284">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8284">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8285">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8285">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8286">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8286">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8287">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8287">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8288">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8288">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8289">14-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8289">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8290">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8290">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8291">14-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8291">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8292">N или n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8292">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8293">L или l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8293">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8294">необязательное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8294">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8295">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8295">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8296">необязательное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8296">optional space, dot, or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8297">B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8297">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8298">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8298">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8299">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8299">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8300">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8300">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8301">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8301">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8302">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8302">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8303">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8303">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8304">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8304">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8305">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8305">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8306">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8306">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8307">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8307">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8308">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8308">Keyword_netherlands_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8309">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8309">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8310">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8310">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8311">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8311">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8312">tax getal для wearde tafoege</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8312">wearde tafoege tax getal</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8313">btw n уmer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8313">btw nûmer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8314">btw-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8314">btw-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8315">Номер банковского счета для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8315">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8316">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8316">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8317">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8317">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8318">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8318">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8319">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8319">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8320">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8320">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8321">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8321">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8322">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8322">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8323">От 14 до 16-значного шаблона с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8323">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8324">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8324">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8325">От 14 до 16-значного шаблона с необязательными делегаторами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8325">14-digit to 16-digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8326">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8326">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8327">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8327">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8328">от трех до четырех цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8328">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8329">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8329">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8330">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8330">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8331">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8331">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8332">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8332">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8333">дефис или пробел для параметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8333">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8334">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8334">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8335">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8335">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8336">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8336">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8337">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8337">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8338">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8338">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8339">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8339">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8340">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8340">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8341">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8341">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8342">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8342">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8343">Keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8343">Keyword_new_zealand_bank_account_number</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8349">Номер водительского удостоверения для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8349">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8350">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8350">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8351">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8351">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8352">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8352">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8353">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8353">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8354">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8354">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8355">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8355">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8356">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8356">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8357">восьми символьный букво-цифровая схема</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8357">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8358">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8358">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8359">восьми символьный букво-цифровая схема</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8359">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8360">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8360">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8361">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8361">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8362">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8362">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8363">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8363">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8364">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8364">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8365">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8365">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8366">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8366">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8367">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8367">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8368">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8368">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8369">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8369">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8370">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8370">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8371">Keyword_new_zealand_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8371">Keyword_new_zealand_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8372">driverlicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8372">driverlicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8373">driverlicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8373">driverlicences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8374">driver lic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8374">driver lic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8375">driver licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8375">driver licence</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8436">Номер выручки для новой Зеландии в стране</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8436">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8437">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8437">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8438">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8438">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8439">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8439">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8440">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8440">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8441">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8441">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8442">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8442">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8443">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8443">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8444">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8444">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8445">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8445">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8446">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8446">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8447">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8447">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8448">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8448">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8449">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8449">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8450">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8450">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8451">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8451">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8452">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8452">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8453">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8453">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8454">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8454">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8455">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8455">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8456">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8456">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8457">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8457">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8458">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8458">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8459">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8459">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8460">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8460">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8461">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8461">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8462">ird no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8462">ird no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8463">ird no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8463">ird no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8464">nz ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8464">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8465">новая Зеландия ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8465">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8466">ird number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8466">ird number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8467">inland revenue number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8467">inland revenue number</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8468">Министерство здравоохранения Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8468">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8469">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8469">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8470">три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8470">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8471">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8471">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8472">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), кроме "I" и "O"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8472">three letters (not case-sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8473">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8473">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8474">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8474">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8475">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8475">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8476">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8476">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8477">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8477">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8478">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8478">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8479">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8479">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8480">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8480">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8481">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8481">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8482">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8482">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8483">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8483">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8484">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8484">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8485">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8485">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8486">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8486">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8487">NHI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8487">NHI</span></span>
