## <a name="new-zealand-social-welfare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8498">Номер социальных сетей Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8498">New Zealand social welfare number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8499">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8499">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8500">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8500">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8501">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8501">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8502">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8502">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8503">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8503">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8504">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8504">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8505">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8505">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8506">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8506">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8507">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8507">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8508">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8508">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8509">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8509">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8510">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8510">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8511">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8511">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8512">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8512">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8513">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8513">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8514">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8514">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8515">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8515">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8516">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8516">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8517">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8517">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8518">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8518">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8519">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8519">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8520">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8520">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8521">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8521">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8522">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8522">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8523">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8523">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8524">social welfare #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8524">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8525">social welfare #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8525">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8526">social welfare No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8526">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8527">номер социальных сетей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8527">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8528">swn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8528">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8529">Идентификационный номер для Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8529">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8530">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8530">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8531">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8531">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8532">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8532">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8533">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8533">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8534">шесть цифр в формате ДДММАЙ, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8534">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8535">трехзначный индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8535">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8536">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8536">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8537">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8537">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8538">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8538">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8539">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8539">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8540">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8540">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8541">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8541">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8542">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8542">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8543">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8543">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8544">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8544">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8545">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8545">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8546">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8546">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8547">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8547">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_norway_id_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8548">Keyword_norway_id_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8548">Keyword_norway_id_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8549">Personal identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8549">Personal identification number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8551">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8551">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8552">Идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8552">Identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8553">Personnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8553">Personnummer</span></span>

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8555">Единый многонамерный идентификационный номер для Филиппин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8555">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8556">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8556">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8557">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8557">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8558">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8558">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8559">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8559">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8560">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8560">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8561">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8561">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8562">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8562">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8563">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8563">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8564">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8564">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8565">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8565">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8566">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8566">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8567">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8567">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8568">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8568">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8569">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8569">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8570">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8570">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8571">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8571">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8572">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8572">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8573">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8573">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8574">UMID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8574">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8575">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8575">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8576">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8576">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8577">Номер водительского удостоверения для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8577">Poland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8578">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8578">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8579">14 цифр, содержащих две косой черты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8579">14 digits containing two forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8580">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8580">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8581">14 цифр и две косой черты:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8581">14 digits and two forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8582">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8582">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8583">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8583">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8584">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8584">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8585">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8585">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8586">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8586">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8587">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8587">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8588">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8588">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8589">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8589">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8590">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8590">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8591">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8591">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8592">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8592">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8716">Удостоверение личности для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8716">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8717">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8717">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8718">три буквы и шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8718">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8719">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8719">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8720">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8720">three letters (not case-sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8721">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8721">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8722">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8722">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8723">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8723">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8724">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8724">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8725">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8725">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8726">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8726">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8727">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8727">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8728">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8728">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8729">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8729">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8730">Dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8730">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8731">Numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8731">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8732">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8732">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8733">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8733">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8734">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8734">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8735">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8735">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8736">dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8736">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8737">os.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8737">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8738">Национальный ИД для Польша (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8738">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8739">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8739">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8740">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8740">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8741">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8741">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8742">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения в формате YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8742">six digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8743">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8743">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8744">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8744">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8745">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8745">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8746">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8746">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8747">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8747">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8748">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8748">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8749">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8749">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8750">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8750">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8751">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8751">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8752">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8752">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8753">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8753">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8754">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8754">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8755">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8755">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_pesel_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8756">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8756">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8757">dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8757">dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8758">dowódosobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8758">dowódosobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8759">niepowtarzalny numer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8759">niepowtarzalny numer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8760">niepowtarzalnynumer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8760">niepowtarzalnynumer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8761">nr.-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8761">nr.-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8762">nr-pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8762">nr-pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8763">numer identyfcyjny</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8763">numer identyfikacyjny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8764">pesel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8764">pesel</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8765">tosamoraswej</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8765">tożsamości narodowej</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8766">Номер паспорта гражданина Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8766">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8767">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8767">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8768">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8768">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8769">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8769">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8770">две буквы и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8770">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8771">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8771">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8772">Две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8772">Two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8773">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8773">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8774">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8774">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8775">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8775">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8776">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8776">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8777">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8777">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8778">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8778">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8779">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8779">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8780">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_passport_date` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8780">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8781">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8781">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8782">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8782">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8783">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8783">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8784">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8784">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_polish_national_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8785">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8785">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8786">Функция находит `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8786">The function `Func_polish_passport_number_v2` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8787">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8787">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number_v2" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8788">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8788">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8789">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8789">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8793">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8793">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8794">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8794">passportno</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8797">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8797">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8798">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8798">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8799">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8799">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_polish_national_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8800">Keyword_polish_national_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8800">Keyword_polish_national_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8801">numer paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8801">numer paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8802">numery paszportów</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8802">numery paszportów</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8805">nr.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8805">nr.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8806">paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8806">paszportu</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_date"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8810">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8810">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8811">дата проблемы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8811">date of issue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8812">дата окончания срока действия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8812">date of expiry</span></span>


## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8813">Номер REGON для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8813">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8814">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8814">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8815">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8815">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8816">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8816">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8817">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8817">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8818">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8818">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8819">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8819">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8820">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8820">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8821">9-значный или 14-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8821">9-digit or 14-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8822">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8822">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8823">девятизначное или 14-значное число:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8823">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8824">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8824">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8825">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8825">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8826">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8826">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8827">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8827">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8828">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8828">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8829">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8829">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8830">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8830">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8831">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8831">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8832">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8832">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8833">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_polish_regon_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8833">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8834">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8834">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8835">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8835">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8836">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8836">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8838">regon id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8838">regon id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8839">статистический номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8839">statistical number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8840">статистический ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8840">statistical id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8841">статистическая нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8841">statistical no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8842">regon number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8842">regon number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8843">regonid #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8843">regonid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8844">regonno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8844">regonno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8845">company id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8845">company id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8846">companyid #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8846">companyid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8847">companyidno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8847">companyidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8848">numer statystyczny</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8848">numer statystyczny</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8849">numeru regon</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8849">numeru regon</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8850">numerstatystyczny #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8850">numerstatystyczny#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8851">numeruregon #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8851">numeruregon#</span></span>


## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8852">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8852">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8853">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8853">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8854">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8854">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8855">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8855">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8856">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8856">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8857">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8857">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8858">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8858">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8859">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8859">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8860">11 цифр без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8860">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8861">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8861">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8862">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8862">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8863">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8863">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8864">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8864">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8865">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8865">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8866">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8866">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8867">Функция находит  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8867">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8868">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8868">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8898">Номер карты гражданина Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8898">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8899">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8899">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8900">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8900">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8901">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8901">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8902">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8902">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8903">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8903">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8904">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8904">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8905">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8905">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8906">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8906">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8907">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8907">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8908">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8908">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8909">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8909">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_portugal_citizen_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8910">Keyword_portugal_citizen_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8910">Keyword_portugal_citizen_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8911">de identidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8911">bilhete de identidade</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8913">citizen card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8913">citizen card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8914">номер документа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8914">document number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8915">documento de identificação</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8915">documento de identificação</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8916">id number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8916">id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8917">identification no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8917">identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8918">identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8918">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8919">identity card no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8919">identity card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8920">номер удостоверения личности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8920">identity card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8921">national id card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8921">national id card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8925">número de identificação fiscal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8925">número de identificação fiscal</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8927">номер bi в Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8927">portugal bi number</span></span>


## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8928">Номер водительского удостоверения для Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8928">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8929">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8929">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8930">два шаблона: две буквы, за которыми следуют 5–8 цифр со специальными символами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8930">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8931">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8931">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8932">Шаблон 1: две буквы, за которыми следуют 5/6 со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8932">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8933">Две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8933">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8934">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8934">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8935">Пять или шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8935">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8936">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8936">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8937">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8937">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8938">Шаблон 2: одна буква, за которой следуют 6/8 цифр со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8938">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8939">Одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8939">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8940">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8940">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8941">Шесть или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8941">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8942">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8942">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8943">одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8943">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8944">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8944">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8945">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8945">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8946">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8946">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8947">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8947">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8948">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8948">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-8949">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-8949">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9081">Номер паспорта гражданина Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9081">Portugal passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9082">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9082">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9083">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9083">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9084">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9084">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9085">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9085">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9086">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9086">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9087">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9087">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9088">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9088">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9089">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9089">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9090">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9090">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9091">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9091">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9092">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9092">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9093">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9093">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9094">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_eu_passport_date1` ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9094">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9095">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9095">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9096">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9096">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9097">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9097">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="080a52fd-a7bc-431e-b54d-51f08f59db11" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9124">Идентификационный номер налога для Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9124">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9125">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9125">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9126">девять цифр с необязательными пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9126">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9127">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9127">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9128">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9128">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9129">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9129">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9130">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9130">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9131">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9131">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9132">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9132">three digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9133">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9133">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9134">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9134">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9135">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9135">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9136">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9136">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9137">Функция находит  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9137">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9138">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9138">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9139">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9139">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9140">Функция находит  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9140">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9141">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9141">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9142">Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9142">Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9143">cpf #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9143">cpf#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9144">cpf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9144">cpf</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9145">nif #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9145">nif#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9146">nif</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9146">nif</span></span>

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9165">Номер водительского удостоверения в Румынии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9165">Romania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9166">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9166">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9167">один символ, за которым следует восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9167">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9168">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9168">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9169">один символ, за которым следует восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9169">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9170">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9170">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9171">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9171">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9172">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9172">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9173">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9173">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9174">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9174">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9175">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9175">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9176">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9176">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9177">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9177">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9305">Личный числовой код Румынии (CNP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9305">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9306">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9306">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9307">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9307">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9308">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9308">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9309">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9309">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9310">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9310">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9311">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9311">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9312">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9312">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9313">13 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9313">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9314">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9314">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9315">одна цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9315">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9316">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9316">six digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9317">две цифры, которые могут быть 01–52 или 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9317">two digits, which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9318">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9318">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9319">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9319">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9320">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9320">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9321">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9321">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9322">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9322">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9323">Функция находит  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9323">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9324">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9324">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9325">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9325">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9326">Функция находит  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9326">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9377">Номер паспорта гражданина Румынии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9377">Romania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9378">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9378">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9379">восемь или девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9379">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9380">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9380">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9381">восемь или девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9381">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9382">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9382">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9383">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9383">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9384">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9384">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9385">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9385">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9386">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9386">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9387">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9387">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9388">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM YY (пример: 01 FEB/FEB 10) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9388">The regular expression `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (Example- 01 FEB/FEB 10) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9389">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9389">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9390">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9390">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9391">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9391">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5d31b90c-7fe2-4a76-a14b-767b8fd19d6c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
