## <a name="russia-passport-number-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9409">Внутренний номер паспорта гражданина России</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9409">Russia passport number domestic</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9413">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9413">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9414">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9414">records management</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9419">10-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9419">10-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9420">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9420">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9421">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9421">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9427">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9427">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9428">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9428">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9429">Regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9429">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9430">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9430">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9465">Regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9465">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <Entity id="ac5f4878-75e4-4b82-af2d-02e13ea9f411" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International" />

        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9483">Национальный идентификатор для Саудовской Аравии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9483">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9484">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9484">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9485">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9485">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9486">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9486">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9487">10 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9487">10 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9488">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9488">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9489">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9489">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9490">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9490">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9491">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9491">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9492">регулярное выражение Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9492">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9493">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9493">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9494">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9494">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9495">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9495">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9496">Identification Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9496">Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9497">I card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9497">I card number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9498">ID number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9498">ID number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9499">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9499">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span></span> 

   
## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9500">Номер удостоверения личности для национальной регистрации Сингапура (NRIC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9500">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9501">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9501">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9502">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9502">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9503">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9503">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9504">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9504">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9505">буква "F", "G", "S" или "T" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9505">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9506">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9506">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9507">алфавитная проверочные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9507">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9508">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9508">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9509">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9509">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9510">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9510">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9511">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9511">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9512">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9512">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9513">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_singapore_nric;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9513">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9514">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9514">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9515">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9515">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9516">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9516">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9517">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9517">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9528">Номер водительского удостоверения для Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9528">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9529">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9529">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9530">один символ, за которым следует семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9530">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9531">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9531">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9532">один символ, за которым следует семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9532">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9533">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9533">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9534">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9534">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9535">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9535">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9536">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9536">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9537">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9537">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9538">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9538">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9539">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9539">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9540">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9540">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9666">Персональный номер для Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9666">Slovakia personal number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9667">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9667">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9668">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9668">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9669">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9669">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9670">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9670">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9671">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9671">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9672">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9672">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9673">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9673">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9674">девять или десять цифр, содержащих необязательные знаки backslash</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9674">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9675">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9675">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9676">шесть цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9676">six digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9677">необязательная косая черта (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9677">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9678">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9678">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9679">одна необязательная проверотельная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9679">one optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9680">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9680">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9681">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9681">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9682">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9682">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9683">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9683">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9684">Функция находит  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9684">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9685">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9685">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9686">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9686">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9687">Функция находит  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9687">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9734">Номер паспорта гражданина Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9734">Slovakia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9735">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9735">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9736">одна цифра или буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9736">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9737">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9737">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9738">одна цифра или буква (без чувствительность к букве), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9738">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9739">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9739">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9740">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9740">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9741">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9741">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9742">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9742">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9743">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9743">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9744">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9744">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9745">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_eu_passport_date1` ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9745">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9746">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9746">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9747">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9747">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9748">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9748">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="238e1f08-d80e-4793-af33-9b57918335b7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9770">Номер водительского удостоверения для Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9770">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9771">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9771">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9772">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9772">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9773">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9773">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9774">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9774">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9775">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9775">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9776">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9776">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9777">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9777">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9778">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9778">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9779">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9779">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9780">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9780">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9907">Уникальный номер гражданина Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9907">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9908">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9908">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9909">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9909">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9910">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9910">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9911">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9911">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9912">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9912">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9913">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9913">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9914">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9914">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9915">13 цифр без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9915">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9916">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9916">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9917">13 цифр в указанном шаблоне:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9917">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9918">семь цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (DDMMLLL), где "LLL" соответствует последним трем цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9918">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9919">две цифры, соответствующие области рождения "50"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9919">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9920">три цифры, соответствующие комбинации пола и серийного номера для людей, которые были в один день (000–499 для детей и 500–999 для детей)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9920">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9921">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9921">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9922">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9922">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9923">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9923">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9924">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9924">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9925">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9925">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9926">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9926">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9927">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9927">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9928">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9928">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9929">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9929">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9957">Номер паспорта гражданина Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9957">Slovenia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9958">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9958">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9959">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9959">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9960">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9960">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9961">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9961">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9962">буква "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9962">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9963">одна буква в верхнем регистре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9963">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9964">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9964">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9965">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9965">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9966">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9966">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9967">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9967">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9968">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9968">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9969">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9969">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9970">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9970">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9971">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_eu_passport_date1` ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9971">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9972">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9972">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9973">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9973">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9974">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9974">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="235b7976-7bbe-4df5-bb40-08678e749d1a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9975">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9975">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9985">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9985">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9986">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9986">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9987">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9987">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9997">Идентификационный номер налога для Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9997">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9998">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9998">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-9999">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-9999">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10000">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10000">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10001">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10001">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10002">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10002">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10003">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10003">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10004">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10004">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10005">восемь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10005">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10006">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10006">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10007">одна цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10007">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10008">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10008">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10009">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10009">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10010">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10010">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10011">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10011">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10012">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10012">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10013">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10013">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10014">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10014">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10015">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10015">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10016">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10016">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10017">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10017">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10041">Идентификационный номер для Южной Африки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10041">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10042">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10042">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10043">13 цифр, которые могут содержать пробелы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10043">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10044">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10044">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10045">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10045">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10046">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10046">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10047">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10047">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10048">индикатор гражданства из одной цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10048">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10049">цифра "8" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10049">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10050">одна цифра, которая является цифрой контрольной суммы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10050">one digit, which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10051">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10051">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10052">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10052">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10053">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10053">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10054">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10054">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10055">функция Func_south_africa_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10055">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10056">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_africa_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10056">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10057">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10057">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10058">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10058">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_africa_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10059">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10059">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10060">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10060">Identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10061">ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10061">ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10062">Идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10062">Identification</span></span> 
   
## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10063">Регистрационный номер резидента Южной Кореи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10063">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10064">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10064">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10065">13 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10065">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10066">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10066">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10067">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10067">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10068">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10068">six digits in the format YYMMDD, which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10069">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10069">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10070">одна цифра, определяемая возрастом и полом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10070">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10071">четырехзначный код региона рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10071">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10072">одна цифра, используемая для различения людей, для которых предыдущие числа идентичны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10072">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10073">контрольная цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10073">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10074">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10074">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10075">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10075">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10076">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10076">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10077">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10077">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10078">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10078">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10079">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_korea_resident_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10079">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10080">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10080">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10081">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10081">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10082">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10082">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10083">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10083">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10084">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10084">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10085">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10085">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10086">National ID card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10086">National ID card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10087">Citizen's Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10087">Citizen's Registration Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10088">Jumin deungnok beonho</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10088">Jumin deungnok beonho</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10089">RRN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10089">RRN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10090">주민등록번호</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10090">주민등록번호</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10091">Номер водительского удостоверения для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10091">Spain driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10092">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10092">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10093">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10093">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10094">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10094">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10095">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10095">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10096">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10096">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10097">одна цифра или буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10097">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10098">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10098">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10099">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10099">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10100">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10100">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10101">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10101">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10102">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10102">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10103">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10103">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10104">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10104">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10105">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10105">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10239">DNI для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10239">Spain DNI</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10240">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10240">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10241">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10241">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10242">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10242">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10243">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10243">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10244">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10244">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10245">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10245">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10246">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10246">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10247">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10247">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10248">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10248">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10249">семь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10249">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10250">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10250">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10251">Необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10251">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10252">одна контрольная буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10252">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10253">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10253">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10254">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10254">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10255">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10255">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10256">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10256">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10257">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10257">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10258">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10258">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10259">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10259">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10260">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10260">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10284">Номер паспорта гражданина Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10284">Spain passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10285">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10285">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10286">сочетание букв и чисел из восьми или девяти символов без пробелов или делений.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10286">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10287">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10287">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10288">восьми- или девяти символьное сочетание букв и чисел:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10288">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10289">две цифры или буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10289">two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10290">одна цифра или буква (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10290">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10291">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10291">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10292">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10292">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10293">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10293">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10294">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10294">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10295">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10295">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10296">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10296">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10297">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10297">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10298">Регулярное выражение `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` находит дату в формате ДД-ММ-YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10298">The regular expression `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD-MM-YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10299">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10299">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10300">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10300">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10301">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10301">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d17a57de-9fa5-4e9f-85d3-85c26d89686e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10330">Номер социального обеспечения Испании (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10330">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10331">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10331">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10332">11–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10332">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10333">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10333">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10334">11–12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10334">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10335">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10335">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10336">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10336">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10337">семь-восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10337">seven to eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10338">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10338">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10339">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10339">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10340">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10340">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10341">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10341">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10342">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10342">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10343">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10343">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10344">функция Func_spanish_social_security_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10344">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10345">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10345">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10346">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10346">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10347">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10347">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10348">функция Func_spanish_social_security_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10348">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10349">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10349">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- Spain SSN -->
    <Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
