- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10357">número de la seguridad social</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10357">número de la seguridad social</span></span>

## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10358">Идентификационный номер налога для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10358">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10359">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10359">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10360">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10360">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10361">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10361">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10362">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10362">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10363">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10363">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10364">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10364">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10365">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10365">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10366">семь или восемь цифр и одна или две буквы в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10366">seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10367">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10367">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10368">Испанские персональные лица с национальные удостоверения личности для Испании:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10368">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10369">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10369">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10370">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10370">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10371">Нерезиденты без национального удостоверения личности для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10371">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10372">одна буква в верхнем регистре "L" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10372">one uppercase letter "L" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10373">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10373">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10374">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10374">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10375">Resident Resident Residents under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10375">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10376">одна буква в верхнем регистре "K" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10376">one uppercase letter "K" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10377">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10377">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10378">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10378">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10379">Подмена идентификационных номеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10379">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10380">одна буква в верхнем регистре, которая является "X", "Y" или "Z" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10380">one uppercase letter that is "X", "Y", or "Z" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10381">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10381">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10382">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10382">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10383">Подмены без идентификационных номеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10383">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10384">одна буква в верхнем регистре с буквой "M" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10384">one uppercase letter that is "M" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10385">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10385">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10386">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10386">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10387">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10387">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10388">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10388">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10389">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10389">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10390">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10390">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10391">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10391">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10392">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10392">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10393">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10393">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10394">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10394">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="10f0d113-b0e1-47dc-872a-a4f45b9376a3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10425">SQL Server подключения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10425">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10426">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10426">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10427">Строка "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в шаблоне ниже.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10427">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10428">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10428">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10429">строка "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10429">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10430">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10430">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10431">строка "Password" или "pwd", где "pwd" не предшествует строчная буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10431">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" isn't preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10432">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10432">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10433">любой символ, который не является знаком доллара ($), символом процента (%), больше символа (>), в символе (@), кавычках ("), точка с зазнаковкой (;), левая скобка ([) или левая скобка ({)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10433">any character that isn't a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10434">любое сочетание 7–128 символов, которые не являются точками с за точками (;) косая черта (/) или кавычка ()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10434">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10435">точка с зачетом (;) или кавычка (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10435">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10436">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10436">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10437">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10437">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10438">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10438">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10439">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10439">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10440">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10440">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10441">Ключевое слово из CEP_GlobalFilter не найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10441">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter isn't found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10442">Регулярное выражение CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10442">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10443">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords не находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10443">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords doesn't find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10444">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10444">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10445">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10445">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10446">some-password</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10446">some-password</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10447">somepassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10447">somepassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10448">secretPassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10448">secretPassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10449">пример</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10449">sample</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_passwordplaceholder"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10450">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10450">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10451">(Обратите внимание, что технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10451">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10452">Пароль или пробелы, за которыми следуют 0-2 пробела, знаки равного (=), 0-2 пробела и звездочка (\*) -OR-</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10452">Password or pwd followed by 0-2 spaces, an equal sign (=), 0-2 spaces, and an asterisk (\*) -OR-</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10453">Пароль или pwd, за которым следует:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10453">Password or pwd followed by:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10454">Знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10454">Equal sign (=)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10455">Символ "Меньше символа" (<)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10455">Less than symbol (<)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10456">Любое сочетание из 1–200 символов, которые являются буквами верхнего или нижнего регистра, цифрами, звездочкой (\*), дефисом (-), подчеркнутой (_) или символом белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10456">Any combination of 1-200 characters that are upper- or lowercase letters, digits, an asterisk (\*), hyphen (-), underline (_), or whitespace character</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10457">Символ "Больше" (>)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10457">Greater than symbol (>)</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_commonexamplekeywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10458">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10458">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10459">(Обратите внимание, что технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10459">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10471">Номер водительского удостоверения для Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10471">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10472">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10472">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10473">десять цифр, содержащих дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10473">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10474">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10474">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10475">десять цифр, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10475">ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10476">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10476">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10477">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10477">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10478">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10478">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10479">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10479">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10480">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10480">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10481">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10481">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10482">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10482">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10483">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10483">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10484">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10484">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10617">Национальный ИД Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10617">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10618">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10618">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10619">10 или 12 цифр и дополнительный разделитель.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10619">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10620">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10620">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10621">10 или 12 цифр с необязательным разделителем</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10621">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10622">две цифры (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10622">two digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10623">Шесть цифр в формате даты ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10623">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10624">либо "-" или "+" (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10624">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10625">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10625">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10626">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10626">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10627">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10627">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10628">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10628">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10629">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10629">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10630">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10630">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10631">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10631">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10632">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10632">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10633">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10633">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10634">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10634">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10635">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10635">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10654">Номер паспорта гражданина Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10654">Sweden passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10655">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10655">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10656">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10656">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10657">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10657">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10658">восемь последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10658">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10659">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10659">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10660">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10660">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10661">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10661">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10662">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10662">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10663">регулярное выражение Regex_sweden_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10663">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10664">ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keyword_sweden_passport` найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10664">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10665">регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10665">the regular expression `Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date` finds a date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (01 JAN/JAN 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10666">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10666">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10667">регулярное выражение Regex_sweden_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10667">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10668">ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keyword_sweden_passport` найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10668">a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keyword_sweden_passport` is found.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10704">Номер социального обеспечения швеции или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10704">Sweden social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10705">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен только в номере социального обеспечения ЕС или типе конфиденциальной информации эквивалентного ИД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10705">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10706">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10706">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10707">12 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10707">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10708">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10708">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10709">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10709">12 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10710">восемь цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYYYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10710">eight digits that correspond to the birth date (YYYYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10711">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру, где:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10711">three digits that correspond to a serial number where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10712">Последняя цифра в серийном номере указывает пол по назначению нечетного номера для самца и четного номера для женщина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10712">the last digit in the serial number indicates gender by the assignment of an odd number for male and an even number for female</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10713">До 1990 г. назначение серийного номера соответствовало округу, в котором был замещетель номера.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10713">Before 1990, the assignment of a serial number corresponded to the county where the bearer of the number was born.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10714">Или (если они были до 1947 г.), где они были, согласно налоговым записям, 1 января 1947 г. с особым кодом (обычно 9 в качестве седьмой цифры) для угона.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10714">Or (if born before 1947) where they had been living, according to tax records, on January 1, 1947, with a special code (usually 9 as the seventh digit) for immigrants.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10715">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10715">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10716">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10716">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10717">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10717">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10718">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10718">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10719">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 85 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10719">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10720">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10720">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10721">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10721">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10722">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 75 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10722">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10723">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10723">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10739">Идентификационный номер налога для Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10739">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10740">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10740">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10741">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10741">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10742">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10742">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10743">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10743">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10744">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10744">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10745">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10745">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10746">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10746">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10747">10 цифр и символ в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10747">10 digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10748">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10748">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10749">10 цифр и символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10749">10 digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10750">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10750">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10751">знак "плюс" или "минус"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10751">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10752">три цифры, которые делают идентификационный номер уникальным, где:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10752">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10753">для номеров, выдавшихся до 1990 г., седьмая и восьмая цифры определяют округ рождения или инородных людей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10753">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10754">цифра в девятой позиции указывает пол по нечетным для самцов или даже для самцов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10754">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10755">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10755">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10756">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10756">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10757">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10757">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10758">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10758">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10759">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10759">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10760">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10760">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10761">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10761">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10762">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10762">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10763">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10763">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10774">tax identification no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10774">tax identification no</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10777">tax no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10777">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10778">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10778">tax number</span></span>

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10789">Код SWIFT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10789">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10790">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10790">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10791">четыре буквы, за которыми следуют от 5 до 31 буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10791">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10792">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10792">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10793">четыре буквы, за которыми следуют 5–31 буква или цифры:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10793">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10794">4-буква банковского кода (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10794">four-letter bank code (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10795">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10795">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10796">4–28 букв или цифр (основной номер банковского счета, BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10796">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10797">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10797">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10798">от одной до трех букв или цифр (оставшаяся часть BBAN);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10798">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10799">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10799">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10800">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10800">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10801">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10801">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10802">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10802">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10803">регулярное выражение Regex_swift находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10803">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10804">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_swift.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10804">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10841">Номер ADV для SSN в Швейцарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10841">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10842">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10842">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10843">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10843">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10844">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10844">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10845">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10845">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10846">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10846">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10847">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10847">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10848">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10848">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10849">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10849">13-digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10850">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10850">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10851">13-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10851">13-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10852">три цифры — 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10852">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10853">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10853">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10854">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10854">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10855">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10855">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10856">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10856">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10857">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10857">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10858">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10858">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10859">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10859">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10860">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10860">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10861">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10861">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10862">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10862">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10863">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10863">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10864">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10864">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10865">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10865">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10866">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10866">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10887">Национальный идентификационный номер для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10887">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10888">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10888">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10889">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10889">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10890">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10890">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10891">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10891">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10892">одна буква (на английском языке без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10892">one letter (in English, not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10893">цифра "1" или "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10893">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10894">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10894">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10895">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10895">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10896">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10896">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10897">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10897">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10898">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10898">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10899">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10899">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10900">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwanese_national_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10900">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10901">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10901">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10902">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10902">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10903">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10903">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10904">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10904">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10905">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10905">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10906">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10906">Keyword_taiwan_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10907">身份證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10907">身份證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10908">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10908">身份證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10909">身份證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10909">身份證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10910">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10910">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10911">身分證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10911">身分證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10912">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10912">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10913">身分證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10913">身分證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10914">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10914">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10915">身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10915">身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10916">國民身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10916">國民身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10917">簽名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10917">簽名</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10918">蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10918">蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10919">簽名或蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10919">簽名或蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10920">簽章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10920">簽章</span></span>   
   
## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10921">Номер паспорта гражданина Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10921">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10922">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10922">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10923">биометрический номер паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10923">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10924">не биометрический номер паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10924">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10925">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10925">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10926">биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10926">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10927">символ "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10927">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10928">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10928">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10929">не биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10929">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10930">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10930">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10931">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10931">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10932">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10932">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10933">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10933">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10934">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10934">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10935">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10935">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10936">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10936">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10937">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10937">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10938">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10938">Keyword_taiwan_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10939">ROC passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10939">ROC passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10940">Passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10940">Passport number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10941">Passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10941">Passport no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10942">Passport Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10942">Passport Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10943">Passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10943">Passport #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10944">护照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10944">护照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10945">中華民國護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10945">中華民國護照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10946">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10946">Zhōnghuá Mínguó hùzhào</span></span>
   
## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10947">Номер сертификата жителя Тайваня (ARC/TARC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10947">Taiwan-resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10948">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10948">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10949">10 букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10949">10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10950">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10950">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10951">10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10951">10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10952">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10952">two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10953">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10953">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10954">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10954">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10955">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10955">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10956">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10956">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10957">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10957">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10958">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10958">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10959">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10959">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10960">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10960">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10961">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10961">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10962">Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10962">Resident Certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10964">Resident Cert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10964">Resident Cert.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10965">Identification card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10965">Identification card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10966">Alien Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10966">Alien Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10967">ARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10967">ARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10968">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10968">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10969">TARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10969">TARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10970">居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10970">居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10971">外僑居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10971">外僑居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10972">台灣地區居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10972">台灣地區居留證</span></span> 

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10973">Идентификационный код для тайских пользователей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10973">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10974">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10974">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10975">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10975">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10976">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10976">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10977">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10977">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10978">первая цифра не является нулем или девятью</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10978">first digit isn't zero or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10979">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10979">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10980">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10980">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10981">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10981">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10982">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10982">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10983">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10983">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10984">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10984">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10985">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10985">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10986">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10986">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10987">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10987">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10988">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10988">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_thai_citizen_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10989">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10989">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span></span>

## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10996">Идентификационный номер гражданина Турецкий</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10996">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10997">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10997">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10998">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10998">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-10999">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-10999">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11000">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11000">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11001">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11001">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11002">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11002">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11003">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11003">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11004">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11004">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11005">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11005">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11006">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Turkish_National_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11006">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11007">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11007">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11008">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11008">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11009">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11009">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11010">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11010">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11011">TC Kim kim</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11011">TC Kimlik No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11012">TC Kim numaras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11012">TC Kimlik numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11013">Vatanda vat vatk numaras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11013">Vatandaşlık numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11014">Vatanda vat vatk no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11014">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11015">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11015">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11016">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11016">driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11017">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11017">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11018">Сочетание 18 букв и цифр в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11018">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11019">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11019">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11020">18 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11020">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11021">Пять букв (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра "9" в качестве буквы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11021">Five letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11022">Одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11022">One digit.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11023">Пять цифр в формате даты MMDDY для даты рождения.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11023">Five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11024">Седьмый символ приращен на 50, если драйвер является женщина; для экзаменов: от 51 до 62, а не от 01 до 12.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11024">The seventh character is incremented by 50 if driver is female; for exampe, 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11025">Две буквы (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра "9" в качестве буквы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11025">Two letters (not case-sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11026">Пять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11026">Five digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11027">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11027">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11028">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11028">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11029">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11029">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11030">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11030">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11031">Функция находит `Func_uk_drivers_license` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11031">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11032">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11032">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11033">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11033">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11034">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11034">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11035">Функция находит `Func_uk_drivers_license` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11035">The function `Func_uk_drivers_license` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11036">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11036">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true" >
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```
