## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11157">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11157">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11158">roll number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11158">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11159">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11159">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11160">две буквы, за которыми следуют 1–4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11160">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11161">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11161">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11162">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют 1-4 числа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11162">two letters (not case-sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11163">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11163">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11164">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11164">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11165">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11165">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11166">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11166">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11167">регулярное выражение Regex_uk_electoral находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11167">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11168">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_electoral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11168">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11169">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11169">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11170">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11170">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11171">council nomination</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11171">council nomination</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11172">nomination form</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11172">nomination form</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11173">electoral register</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11173">electoral register</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11174">electoral roll</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11174">electoral roll</span></span>

   
## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11175">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11175">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11176">national health service number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11176">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11177">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11177">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11178">10–17 цифр, разделенных пробелами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11178">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11179">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11179">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11180">10-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11180">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11181">3 или 10 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11181">either 3 or 10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11182">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11182">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11183">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11183">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11184">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11184">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11185">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11185">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11186">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11186">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11187">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11187">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11188">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11188">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11189">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11189">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11190">Функция Func_uk_nhs_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11190">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11191">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11191">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11192">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11192">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11193">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number1;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11193">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11194">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11194">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11195">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11195">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11207">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11207">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span></span>

## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11213">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11213">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11214">national insurance number (NINO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11214">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11215">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации для национального идентификационных номеров ЕС.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11215">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11216">Он доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11216">It's available as a stand-alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11217">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11217">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11218">семь символов или девять символов, разделенных пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11218">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11219">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11219">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11220">два возможных шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11220">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11221">две буквы (допустимые niNOs используют только определенные символы в этом префиксе, который проверяется этим шаблоном; без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11221">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11222">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11222">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11223">либо "A", "B", "C", либо "D" (как и префикс, в суффиксе разрешены только определенные символы, без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11223">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case-sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11224">ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11224">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11225">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11225">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11226">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11226">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11227">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11227">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11228">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11228">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11229">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11229">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11230">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11230">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11231">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11231">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11232">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11232">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11233">"A", "B", "C" или "D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11233">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11234">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11234">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11235">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11235">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11236">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11236">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11237">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11237">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11238">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11238">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11239">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11239">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11240">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11240">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11241">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11241">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11263">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11263">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11264">Уникальный справочный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11264">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11265">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11265">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11266">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11266">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11267">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11267">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11268">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11268">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11269">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11269">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11270">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11270">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11271">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11271">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11272">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11272">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11273">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11273">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11274">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11274">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11275">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11275">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11276">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11276">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11277">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11277">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11278">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11278">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11279">Функция находит  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11279">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11280">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11280">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11300">Номер банковского счета в США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11300">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11301">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11301">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11302">6–17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11302">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11303">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11303">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11304">6–17 последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11304">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11305">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11305">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11306">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11306">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11307">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11307">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11308">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11308">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11309">регулярное выражение Regex_usa_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11309">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11310">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_usa_Bank_Account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11310">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11319">Checking Account No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11319">Checking Account No.</span></span>

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11340">Номер водительского удостоверения для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11340">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11341">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11341">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11342">Зависит от штата.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11342">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11343">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11343">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11344">зависит от состояния , например Нью-Йорк:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11344">depends on the state - for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11345">будут совпадать девять цифр в формате ddd ddd ddd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11345">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11346">девять цифр, например ddddddddd, не будут совпадать.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11346">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11347">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11347">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11348">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11348">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11349">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11349">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11350">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11350">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11351">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11351">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11352">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11352">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11353">обнаружено ключевое слово из списка Keyword_us_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11353">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11354">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11354">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11355">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11355">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11356">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11356">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11357">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11357">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11358">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11358">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11445">Driver's Lic#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11445">Driver's Lic#</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11446">Driver's Lics#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11446">Driver's Lics#</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11447">Driver's License#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11447">Driver's License#</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11448">Driver's Licenses#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11448">Driver's Licenses#</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11449">id card#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11449">id card#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11455">название штата (например, "Нью-Йорк")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11455">state name (for example, "New York")</span></span>

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11456">Идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (ITIN) для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11456">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11457">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11457">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11458">девять цифр, которые начинаются с "9" и содержат цифру "7" или "8" в качестве четвертой цифры, при желании отформатированные с пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11458">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11459">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11459">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11460">отформатированный:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11460">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11461">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11461">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11462">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11462">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11463">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11463">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11464">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11464">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11465">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11465">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11466">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11466">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11467">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11467">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11468">unformatted:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11468">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11469">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11469">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11470">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11470">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11471">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11471">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11472">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11472">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11473">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11473">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11474">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11474">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11475">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11475">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11476">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11476">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11477">Функция Func_formatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11477">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11478">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11478">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11479">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11479">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11480">Функция Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11480">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11481">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11481">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11482">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11482">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11483">Функция Func_formatted_itin или Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11483">The function Func_formatted_itin or Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
    <Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11484">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11484">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11485">Keyword_itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11485">Keyword_itin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11486">налогоплательщик</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11486">taxpayer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11488">tax identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11488">tax identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11489">itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11489">itin</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11490">i.t.i.n.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11490">i.t.i.n.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11491">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11491">ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11494">tax payer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11494">tax payer</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11495">itins</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11495">itins</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11496">ыd</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11496">taxid</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11497">individual taxpayer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11497">individual taxpayer</span></span> 


## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11498">Номер социального обеспечения (SSN) для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11498">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11499">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11499">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11500">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11500">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11501">Есть SSN выдан до середины 2011 г., он отличается строгим форматированием, при котором определенные части номера должны входить в указанные диапазоны (при этом нет контрольной суммы).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11501">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11502">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11502">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11503">четыре функции искать SSNs в четырех различных шаблонах:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11503">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11504">Func_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием с тире или пробелами, выданные до 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11504">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11505">Func_unformatted_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием, выданные до 2011 г. (без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр — ццццццццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11505">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11506">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит SSN с тире или пробелами, выданные после 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11506">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11507">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит SSN без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр, выданные после 2011 г. (ццццццццц).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11507">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11508">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11508">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11509">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11509">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11510">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11510">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11511">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11511">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11512">Функция Func_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11512">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11513">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11513">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11514">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11514">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11515">Функция Func_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11515">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11516">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11516">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11517">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11517">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11518">Функция Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11518">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11519">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11519">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11520">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 55 % верно обнаружила этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в пределах ближайших 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11520">A DLP policy is 55% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11521">Функция Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11521">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11522">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11522">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11523">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11523">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11524">Keyword_ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11524">Keyword_ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11525">Номер SSA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11525">SSA Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11526">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11526">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11527">social security #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11527">social security #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11528">social security #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11528">social security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11529">social security no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11529">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11530">Social Security#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11530">Social Security#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11531">Soc Sec</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11531">Soc Sec</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11532">SSN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11532">SSN</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11533">SSNS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11533">SSNS</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11534">SSN #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11534">SSN#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11535">SS #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11535">SS#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11536">SSID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11536">SSID</span></span>
   
## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11537">США и Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11537">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11538">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11538">passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11539">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11539">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11540">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11540">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11541">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11541">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11542">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11542">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11543">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11543">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11544">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11544">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11545">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11545">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11546">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11546">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11547">функция Func_usa_uk_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11547">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11548">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11548">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11549">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_passport_date` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11549">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11550">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11550">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11551">функция Func_usa_uk_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11551">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11552">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11552">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. / U.K. Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11568">Внутренний паспорт гражданина Украины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11568">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11574">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11574">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11575">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11575">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11576">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11576">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11577">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11577">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11578">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11578">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11579">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11579">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11580">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11580">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11581">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11581">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11582">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11582">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11583">Regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11583">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11584">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11584">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">

        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ukraine-passport-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11593">Паспорт гражданина Украины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11593">Ukraine passport international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11594">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11594">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11595">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11595">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11596">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11596">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11597">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11597">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11598">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11598">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11599">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11599">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11600">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11600">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11601">восьми-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11601">eight-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11602">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11602">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11603">восьми-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11603">eight-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11604">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11604">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11605">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11605">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11606">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11606">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11607">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11607">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11608">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11608">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11609">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11609">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11610">Regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11610">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11611">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11611">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport International -->
      <Entity id="cfbe032d-22e0-4f28-ab68-d66e9641f1e2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11612">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11612">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ukraine_passport_international"></a><span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11613">Keyword_ukraine_passport_international</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11613">Keyword_ukraine_passport_international</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11614">паспорта гражданина Украины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11614">ukraine passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11615">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11615">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11616">passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11616">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11617">паспорт України</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11617">паспорт України</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="b2b44-11618">номер паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="b2b44-11618">номер паспорта</span></span>
